(88, '2012-01-13 05:12:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120112/201201122212415150.png', 'http://www.pennywise.biz', '18 Pairs of Luvs Infant Socks for $7 + 1-cent s&h', 'Until January 13 at 9 pm ET, Pennywise offers 18 Pairs of Luvs Infant Socks in White for $7.99. Coupon code "DealForGirl1" cuts it to <strong>$6.99</strong>. With <strong>1 cent</strong> for shipping, that''s $17 off, $0.39 per pair, a buck under our April mention, and the lowest total price we could find for this quantity of these socks. They''re available in size 0 to 6 months and 6-18 months.', 8, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(89, '2012-01-13 05:12:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120112/201201122212416568.jpg', 'http://www.shopakira.com/winter-sale/?sort=newest&utm_content=coats%2Band%2Bsweaters', 'Akira coupon: 30% off winter apparel, deals from $8 + $7 s&h', 'Akira cuts <strong>30% off</strong> select winter apparel via coupon code "STAYWARM30". With prices starting at <strong>$8.20</strong> after the discount, that''s among the best offers we''ve seen from Akira. (We saw an extra 50% off sale in November.) Shipping starts at <strong>$6.95</strong>, or get free shipping on orders over $150. Akira carries brands including Mink Pink, Motel Rocks, and more. Deal ends January 15.', 8, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
