(128, '2012-01-13 14:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130702413811.png', 'http://www.disneystore.com/mn/1001152/?CMP=AFL-AffLSGen&att=LSGenAffl&LSID=552179%257C10986768%257CVHhBNVhBb0JDeHNBQUVRVmpAOEFBQUp5', 'Disney Store sale: Up to 63% off select items + 30% off, deals from $2 + $5 s&h', 'Disney Store takes <strong>up to 63% off</strong> over 400 items during its Twice Upon a Year Sale. (The product page reflects the discount.) Plus, coupon code "SALE30" takes an <strong>extra 30% off</strong> clearance items, with no minimum purchase required. With prices starting at <strong>$2.09</strong> after the discount, that beats our mention from three days ago (which only took up to 60% off and lacked the extra percent-off coupon) and is the best deal we''ve seen on these items from Disney in over a year. Shipping starts at <strong>$4.50</strong>, or spend $75 or more and use coupon code "SHIPTODAY" to qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable. Coupon expires January 15.', 8, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(129, '2012-01-13 15:38:50', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130838504857.png', 'http://www.rockport.com/', 'Rockport Coupons: 10% off any Orer, More', '<li> FREE SHIPPING </li> Available Rockport Coupons and Rockport Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>10% off Entier Order</b><br />Use Rockport Coupon Code WELCOME10 or WELCOMETXT10<br /><li>20% off everyday at any U.S. Reebok or Rockport Outlet Store for AAA Members In-store Printable Rockport Coupon<br /><li>Free Shipping on All Orders <br /><li>Sign up and get 10% off <br />', 6, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(130, '2012-01-13 15:44:08', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130844087667.jpg', '', 'Fredericks of Hollywood extra 50% off', '<p>Frederick&#8217;s of Hollywood is offering <strong>an extra 50% off</strong> clearance sale (Discount applied at checkout) + free shipping on order of $25 or more.</p>', 0, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(131, '2012-01-13 16:02:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130902356168.png', 'http://www.botachtactical.com/ma54elsp80bo.html', 'Magnum Men''s Elite Spider 8" Work Boots for $55 + free shipping', 'Botach Tactical offers the Magnum Men''s Elite Spider 8.0 Work / Tactical 8" Boots in Desert Tan, model no. 5469, for <strong>$55</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s tied with our mention from last week and the lowest total price we could find by $5. (Most places charge $90 or more.) They''re available in most sizes from 7 to 11.5 in medium width, with wide widths available in 7 and 7.5 only.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(132, '2012-01-13 16:02:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130902353338.png', 'http://www.coldwatercreek.com/product-detail/55929/62144/detail.aspx?BPID=17&cm_mmc=Pricegrabber-_-Women''s%20Accessories/Hats/Gloves-_-Generic-_-Generic&srccode=cii_5784816&cpncode=22-195363404-2', 'Coldwater Creek Waterfall Vest for $12 + free shipping', 'Today only, Coldwater Creek offers the Coldwater Creek Women''s Waterfall Vest in seven colors (Navy pictured) for an in-cart price of <b>$11.99</b>. With <b>free shipping</b> via coupon code "WFH3753", that''s $3 under our mention from a week ago and the lowest total price we could find. Sales tax is added where applicable. This soft-knit vest is machine washable and comes to mid-thigh. With a little t.l.c., it might last you for years and years.<p>Of note: Please go chasin'' waterfalls. Don''t stick to the blouses and the tops that you''re used to. We know that you''re gonna dress up your way or not at all, but we think you''re ready for vests.</p>', 4, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(133, '2012-01-13 16:02:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130902369657.png', 'http://www.classicshapewear.com/strech-satin-and-lace-babydoll-set-lz7-p-3293.html', 'Classic Shapewear Women''s Stretch Satin Lingerie Set for $10 + free shipping', 'Classic Shapewear offers its Classic Shapewear Women''s Stretch Satin and Lace Babydoll Set in four colors (Fuchsia pictured) for $39. Coupon code "BABYDOLL" cuts it to <strong>$9.99</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s $29 off and tied with our mention from last week as the lowest total price we could find for the set. It comes with matching thong panties and is available in sizes from M to 3XL. (However, not all size/color combinations are in stock.)', 14, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(134, '2012-01-13 16:32:38', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201130932383939.jpg', 'http://www.everydaysource.com/product/DD/86085', 'Silver Rectangular Stripe Cufflinks for $1 + $3 s&h', 'For its newsletter subscribers only, EverydaySource offers these Silver Rectangular Stripe Cufflinks (pictured) for $5.49. Coupon code "S0112JXTZ" drops it to <strong>$1.49</strong>. With <strong>$2.99</strong> for shipping, that''s tied with our mention from two weeks ago and the lowest total price we could find for comparable cufflinks by $16.', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(135, '2012-01-13 17:02:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131002351096.jpg', 'http://www.urbanoutfitters.com/urban/catalog/faceted_category.jsp?indexStart=0&categories=catalog01_mens&categories2=catalog01_mens_m_trends&categories3=catalog01_mens_m_trends_m_20offshoes&_requestid=44187&cm_mmc=Performics-_-Affiliates-_-dealnews-_-Primary&clickid=0004b66bd2e321a30a4232025ff96ec8', 'Urban Outfitters Foot Therapy Sale: 20% off select shoes', 'Urban Outfitters cuts <b>20% off</b> a selection of men''s and women''s shoes during its Foot Therapy Sale. (Discounted prices are marked on the product page.) That''s the best sale we''ve seen on shoes from Urban Outfitters since November, when it took up to 75% off select shoes. Shipping is a flat <b>$10</b>, but orders over $50 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable. Prices start at <b>$23</b> for women''s shoes and <b>$14</b> for men''s shoes. Sale ends January 16.', 8, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(136, '2012-01-13 17:32:37', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131032376117.png', 'http://www.meritline.com/usb-heating-hands-gloves-heated-warmer-gloves-black-with-white-and-red-stripe---p-58926.aspx?clickid=VHhCcWtnb0JDeGtBQURtWXptd0FBQUsw&source=dealnews', 'USB Heated Warmer Gloves for $4 + free shipping', 'Meritline offers these USB Heated Warmer Gloves for <strong>$3.99</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s tied with our mention from a month ago and $4 below the lowest total price we could find for a similar pair of gloves elsewhere. These cotton gloves plug into a USB port and keep your hands warm while you work and play during the cold winter months. No sizing information is available.<p>Expect this item to take two to three weeks to arrive.</p>', 26, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(137, '2012-01-13 17:32:37', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131032374003.jpg', 'http://us.dockers.com/home/index.jsp', 'Dockers coupon: Buy one non-sale item, get 50% off 2nd', 'At Dockers, buy one regular-priced item and get <strong>50% off</strong> a second regular-priced item via coupon code "HALFOFF". That''s the best BOGO offer we''ve seen from Dockers since November, although that sale stacked with all sale items and included free shipping with no minimum. Shipping adds <b>$7.50</b>, but orders over $50 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable and some exclusions apply. Sale ends January 18 at 2:59 am ET.', 3, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(138, '2012-01-13 17:38:53', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131038532276.jpg', 'http://www.eastbay.com/?SID=8698', 'Eastbay Coupons: 10% off No Minimum, 15% off $75, More', 'Available <b>Eastbay Coupons</b> and Eastbay Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>10% off no minimum</b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon URLEB8N4<br /><li><b>15% off your order of $75 or more </b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon pkebv258 or AFANJI20<br /><li><b>$20 off orders of $120 or more</b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon Code LKS1CP96 <br /><li><b>10% Off $50 or more</b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon AFCHILL1 <br /><li><b>$5 off $50 or more</b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon EMEBFIVE<br /><li><b>15% off your order of $75 or more (up to $15 off)</b><br />Use Eastbay Coupon LKSOLOGY <br /><li><b>Free Shipping On $75</b> [Exp. 01/14]<br />Use Eastbay Coupon IPEBWT27', 6, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(139, '2012-01-13 18:02:40', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131102409079.jpg', 'http://www.josbank.com:80/menswear/shop/ProductDisplayView?storeId=11001&productId=100506&catalogId=10050&ddkey=http:ReferralView', 'Jos. A. Bank Executive Suits for $127, Outerwear for $147 + free shipping', 'Today only, Jos. A. Bank offers select clearance Executive Wool/Cashmere or Flannel Suits for <strong>$127</strong> and select casual outerwear for <strong>$147</strong>, each with <strong>free shipping</strong>. (The sale prices are as shown on the product page.) That puts most items are at the lowest total price we''ve ever seen. Sales tax is added where applicable. Some best bets:<ul><li>Jos. A. Bank Men''s Executive 2-Button Wool/Cashmere Suit with Pleated Trousers for <strong>$127</strong></li><li>Jos. A. Bank Men''s Cashmere Bomber for <strong>$147</strong></li><li>Jos. A. Bank Men''s New Zealand Sheepskin Open Bottom Jacket for <strong>$147</strong></li><li>browse all items in the Jos. A. Bank Deal of the Day</li></ul>', 1, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(140, '2012-01-13 18:08:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131108545556.jpg', 'http://www.dsw.com', 'DSW Coupons: $10 off $49, $20 off $99, $35 off $149 + Free Shipping on $35, More', 'Available DSW Coupons and DSW Coupon Codes:<br />Tips: <b>All Coupons below are stackable. You can stack up to 3 coupons in one order. You might need to be a DSW Rewards member to use the coupon codes (free to join) for some of the coupons to work</b><br /><li><b>$10 off $49, $20 off $99, $35 off $149</b> [Exp. 01/21]<br />Use DSW Coupon INDULGE<br /><li><b>Free SM Cable Knit Rain Boot Liner with womens Rainboot purchase for DSW Rewards Members</b> [Exp. 01/13]<br />* Use DSW Coupon RAINYDAY<br />* You must add women''s rain boot (item # 230830) to cart to redeem the coupon. <br /><li><b>Free Standard Shipping on Orders of $35 or more</b> [Exp. 06/20/12] <br />Use DSW Coupon SHIPR <br /><li><b>500 "Bonus Points" per Pair of Athleic Shoes Online and In-store for DSW Rewards Members</b> [Exp. 01/16]<br />* Details <br /><li>Free Shoes Friday Sweepstakes [Exp. 01/27/12]', 1, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(141, '2012-01-13 18:32:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131132431395.png', 'http://www.lugz.com/', 'Lugz coupon: 35% off all regularly-priced shoes', 'Lugz takes <strong>35% off</strong> all regularly-priced shoes with no minimum purchase required via coupon code "MLK35". That''s one of the best coupons we''ve seen from Lugz in recent months, though we saw 50% off all regularly-priced items four weeks ago (since expired). Shipping starts at <strong>$9.50</strong>. Coupon ends Janaury 16.', 1, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
