(146, '2012-01-13 21:32:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131432416536.jpg', 'http://www.ebags.com/product/delsey/helium-fusion-lite-20-personal-bag/153375?productid=10026514&sourceid=comjfeed&pid=552179&sid=vhhdatbnb0jdehnbquvkudmwrufbqujl', '20% off Delsey Helium Fusion Lite 2.0 Luggage, deals from $20 + free shipping', 'eBags cuts <strong>20% off</strong> a selection of Delsey Helium Fusion Lite 2.0 Luggage via coupon code "EMDTC". (Although it says "Coupons Not Applicable", this coupon code works.) Even better, these bags qualify for <b>free shipping</b>. That''s the best sale we''ve seen on these items from eBags, although many are still less expensive elsewhere. Deal ends January 16.<p>A best bet is the Delsey Helium Fusion Lite 2.0 Personal Bag in Black or Sky Blue for <b>$19.99</b> with <b>free shipping</b> after the above code. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $5. It features a detachable shoulder strap, handles, ID tag, exterior pockets, and more.</p>', 10, 'Dealnews Clothing');
