(147, '2012-01-13 21:32:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131432427658.jpg', 'http://www.championusa.com/?y1=110273&cm_mmc=email-_-20120113-_-NA-_-Site_Promotion&cm_em=no@no.com&SiteId=NKa3hZyYoHA-U.K8UtjiVVl7Q2BWnF4Lqg&cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-NA-_-NA-_-NA&d1=LINKSC', 'Champion: 20% off sitewide, stacks with sale + free shipping', 'Ending today, Champion cuts <strong>20% off</strong> sitewide, including sale items, and offers <b>free shipping</b> on all orders. With items starting at <strong>$4.79</strong> after the discount, that''s the best sale we''ve seen from Champion in a year. Sales tax is added where applicable and some exclusions apply.', 4, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
