(149, '2012-01-13 22:02:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131502481338.jpg', 'http://www.ewatches.com/cust/dailydealsteal.asp?utm_campaign=deals&utm_source=dealnews&utm_medium=cpc&rid=dealnews', 'Swiss Legend Women''s South Beach Watch for $49 + free shipping', 'Today only, eWatches offers the Swiss Legend Women''s South Beach Watch, model no. V91473, for <strong>$49</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $30. It features a stainless steel case, Swiss quartz movement, and water resistance to 330 feet.', 10, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(150, '2012-01-13 22:02:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131502484758.png', 'http://www.ice.com/earrings/silver-earring-prd_esy_106259.jsp?srccode=cii_10043468&cpncode=18-110829846-2', 'ICE.com: $20 off regularly-priced jewelry of $20 or more + free shipping', 'ICE.com takes <strong>$20 off</strong> most regularly-priced orders of $20 or more via coupon code "S20AU". Plus, all items qualify for <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the best dollar-off coupon we''ve seen from ICE.com since three weeks ago, when it took $25 off $25 or more. Note that sale items, clearance, engagement rings, and bridal rings are excluded from the discount. Some best bets after coupon:<ul><li>2-1/5 Carat Multi-Gemstone Sterling Silver Ring for <strong>$25</strong></li><li>Stainless Steel Bar Code Cuff Bracelet for <strong>$30</strong></li><li>Black Agate Sterling Silver Leverback Earrings (pictured) for <strong>$35</strong></li><li>shop for more eligible jewelry at ICE.com</li></ul>', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(151, '2012-01-13 22:32:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201131532483569.png', 'http://gan.doubleclick.net/gan_click?mid=VHhDdzVnb0JDeHNBQUVLRjZNY0FBQURT&lid=41000000001259428&pubid=21000000000054384&adurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ae.com%2Fweb%2Fbrowse%2Fproduct.jsp%3FcatId%3Dcat5180142%26productId%3D2422_5790%26cid%3DAEO_CSE_K65590%26mr%3AreferralID%3D01a9eade-3e31-11e1-8078-001b2166c62d', 'AEO Earbud Earmuffs for $6 + free shipping', 'American Eagle offers its AEO Earbud Earmuffs in Brown or White for the in-cart price of $7.19. Coupon code "11492621" drops it to <b>$5.75</b>. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that''s $14 off and the lowest total price we could find. Sales tax is added where applicable. They features faux fur muffs, faux suede headband, removable earbuds, and microphone. Deal ends January 17.', 8, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
