(221, '2012-01-14 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201132210572803.jpg', 'http://www.bathandbodyworks.com/home/index.jsp?cm_mmc=PJ-_-43764-_-328858677-_-ADZBBW', 'Bath &#038; Body Works up to 75% off + $10 off $30 coupon', '<p> Bath &amp; Body Works is having<strong> up to 75% off</strong> Hello Yellow Sale + <strong>extra $10 off $30 or more</strong> with code <strong>QUACK10</strong>. Free shipping on $50 or more. For in-store purchase use this printable coupon.</p>', 7, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(222, '2012-01-14 05:32:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201132232442791.png', 'http://www.hollisterco.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/ProductDisplay?catalogId=10201&storeId=10251&langId=-1&categoryId=12735&parentCategoryId=12634&topCategoryId=12551&productId=805067', 'Hollister Men''s Sunset Cliffs Jacket for $17 + $8 s&h', 'Hollister offers the Hollister Men''s Sunset Cliffs Jacket in Navy or Red for <strong>$17.38</strong>. With <strong>$8</strong> for shipping, that''s $53 off and the lowest total price we could find. Sales tax is added where applicable. It''s available in sizes S to XL, although not all sizes come in all colors.', 6, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(223, '2012-01-14 05:32:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201132232448004.jpg', 'http://www.originalpenguin.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-opg-Site/default/Product-Show?pid=1DCK0033OP&utm_medium=shoppingengine&utm_source=become', 'Original Penguin Factory Men''s Apparel: 50% off, deals from $10 + $5 s&h', 'Original Penguin cuts <strong>50% off</strong> its Original Penguin Factory Men''s Apparel via coupon code "OPTAKE50". That''s tied with our October mention as the largest discount we''ve seen on these items from Original Penguin. Shipping adds <strong>$5</strong>, but orders of $50 or more qualify for free shipping. Sale items are excluded. After discount, shoes start at <b>$9.99</b>, T-shirts start at <b>$14.50</b>, and jeans start at <b>$34.99</b>. Deal ends January 15.<p>A best bet is this Original Penguin Factory Men''s Striped Polo in Rain Heather (pictured), Blue Bell, or Black Iris for $59.99 before the coupon above, <strong>$29.99</strong> after. With <strong>$5</strong> for shipping, that''s $30 off and the lowest total price we could find. It''s available in sizes S to XXL, although not in all size/color combinations.</p>', 6, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(224, '2012-01-14 05:32:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120113/201201132232443449.jpg', 'http://www.JoesNewBalanceOutlet.com/detail.asp?style=MX416SL&s1=bizrate&s2=DF&s3=MX416SL', 'Joe''s New Balance Outlet: Up to 79% off shoes, apparel, deals from $7 + $5 s&h', 'Joe''s New Balance Outlet cuts <strong>up to 79% off</strong> select men''s and women''s shoes and apparel, with prices starting at <strong>$6.99</strong>. Shipping adds <strong>$4.95</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $75 or more. That''s one of the best sales we''ve seen from Joe''s New Balance Outlet in recent months. (We saw up to 86% off last month, since expired.) Notable deals, with prices after coupon:<ul><li> New Balance Men''s Cool 2 Sleeveless Top for <strong>$15.99</strong></li><li> New Balance Women''s Essential Knit Pants for <strong>$19.99</strong></li><li> New Balance Men''s 416 Cross Training Shoes (pictured) for <strong>$29.99</strong></li><li> New Balance Women''s 759 Running Shoes for <strong>$44.99</strong></li><li>shop Joe''s New Balance Outlet for more buying ideas</li></ul>', 13, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
