(447, '2012-01-16 05:07:12', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152207123766.jpg', 'http://www.abercrombie.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/StoreView?storeId=10051&catalogId=10901&langId=-1', 'Up to 75% OFF Abercrombie & Fitch & Hollister Outwear', '<ul><li> Abercrombie &amp; Fitch &nbsp;and Hollister cuts <strong >up to 75% off</strong> its selection of men''s and women''s outwear. </li><li> For example, Maria long down coat is only $47.94 . </li><li> Free shipping over $100! </li></ul> &nbsp; <p> </p>', 5, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(448, '2012-01-16 05:07:13', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152207122931.jpg', 'http://www.ashford.com/ashford/browse/productDetail.jsp?productId=QT7122903&source=406010001&AID=10983092&PID=1225267&SID=u0t0f0fp67252dd0c0s&PubCID=1899918&LinkName=Ashford+-+Save+up+to+80%25&PubName=dealmoon.com&src=AACJ', 'From $34 Men''s Timberland Watches', '<ul><li> Ashford has a few Men''s Timberland Watches on sale via coupon code <b>SLICKTIMBERLAND </b>+ <b>free shipping</b>.</li><li>The deals： </li><ul><li> Timberland Sandown Chrono Watch <b>$44</b></li><li> Timberland Steprock Digital Chronograph Watch <b>$44</b></li><li> Timberland Portosera Gold Toned Watch <b>$36</b></li><li> Timberland Fastpack White Dial Watch <b>$34</b></li></ul></ul>', 5, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(449, '2012-01-16 05:08:51', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152208513618.gif', 'http://www.shoebuy.com/?cm_mmc=cj-text-_-none-_-none-_-none', 'Shoebuy Coupons: 25% Off Entire Order + Free Shipping, More', '<li> FREE SHIPPING. Free Return Shipping. </li> <li> No Tax. </li> Available <b>Shoebuy Coupons</b> and <b>Shoebuy Promotion Codes</b><br /><li><b>25% Off Entire Order + Free Shipping</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon Code BDAY <br /><li><b>$10 Off Any Purchase + Free Shipping</b> [Exp. 01/15]<br />Use Shoebuy Coupon Code EMLNEWYEAR2012 <br /><li><b>$12 Off $35 Or More</b> [Exp. 01/12]<br />Use Shoebuy Coupon EMLBDAY12 <br /><li><b>20% off Clearance Items plus Free Shipping!</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon BLOWOUT <br /><li><b>$15 off $70, $25 off $100 or $75 off $275</b> [Exp. 01/09]<br />Use Shoebuy Coupon Code EMLMELT12 <br /><li><b>$5 off any purchase</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon COPIOUS065 or ACCESS105 <br /><li><b>15% off Entire Order</b> <br />Use Shoebuy Coupon Code SPRING15 <br /><li> Extra 5% off your first purchase <br />*Extra 5% off when you registe with Shoebuy or for return customers within 60 days of your first purchase<br />* Stackable with other Shoebuy Coupons<br /><li><b>10% off Online</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon SHOEBUY or BONUS or ABILIZER or CHILL or abenity <br /><li><b>$5 off $25 or more</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon ACCESS <br /><li><b>$5 off of $50</b><br />Use Shoebuy Coupon BUY5', 8, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
