epublic Coupon <b>LUXE</b> (Luxe Card Members Only)', 5, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(451, '2012-01-16 05:10:55', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210557271.jpg', 'http://shop.elizabetharden.com/family/index.jsp?categoryId=2779912', 'Elizabeth Arden Gift with Purchase', '<p> <strong> </strong> Elizabeth Arden is having a after Holiday Cyber Beauty Buys event with up to 35% off + free shipping on $40 or more. Plus, you can combine the following percent coupon or Gift with Purchase promotions.</p> <ul> <li>8-Piece best of beauty gift + free shipping with $40 order via code &#8220;<strong>8DEAL</strong>&#8220;</li> <li>20% off entire order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>NEWYEARS20</strong>&#8220;</li> <li> 15-Piece Luxe Collection for $29.5 with any Elizabeth Arden Purchase </li> <li> Free 8-Piece Deluxe Gift + FREE Shipping with ANY $40 order with code <strong>8WONDERS</strong></li> </ul> <p>Note that you can add 33-Piece Holiday Color Collection ($350 value) Just $45 with ANY $27.50 purchase.<strong> </strong>Note that you may combine this offer with above codes to maximize your purchase.<strong><br /> </strong></p>', 5, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(452, '2012-01-16 05:10:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210561494.jpg', 'http://www.drugstore.com/templates/browse/content.asp?catid=112291&aid=333840&aparam=7AJr1csao4Q-X.HLjMyE.R4GHflIVEnuow', 'Beauty.com: Red Carpet Ready set ($185 value) with $150 purchase', '<p> Beauty.com is offering a new Gift With Purchase : get Red Carpet Ready set which includes a black lace bag designed by Marchesa filled with these 17 deluxe samples (total value is over $185) with<strong> </strong> any <strong>$150</strong> Beauty.com purchase.</p>', 13, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(453, '2012-01-16 05:10:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210567485.jpg', 'http://www.thebodyshop-usa.com/linkshare.aspx?siteID=7AJr1csao4Q-LZaZCeNceYZyf5CbFu.D2w&url=http://www.thebodyshop-usa.com/home-fragrance/home-fragrance-oils/spiced-vanilla-home-fragrance-oil.aspx?', 'The Body Shop: holiday scents 60% to 80% off + extra 10% off', '<p> The Body Shop is cutting<strong> 60% to 80% off</strong> select holiday scents, with prices starting at $1. Plus get another 10% off via coupon code &#8220;JOY10&#8243;. Member can save another 10%.  Get free shipping with any order sitewide. For example:</p> <ul> <li> The Body Shop Spiced Vanilla Home Fragrance Oil for <strong>$2</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Cranberry Joy Bubble Bath for <strong>$3</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Candied Ginger Body Scrub for <strong>$4</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Candied Ginger Body Butter for <strong>$5</strong></li> <li>see all discounted holiday scents at The Body Shop </li> </ul>', 11, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(454, '2012-01-16 05:10:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210563857.jpg', 'http://www.gnc.com/family/index.jsp?categoryId=4127856&ab=CMS:HOMEPAGE:CMS:G1', 'GNC select Vitamins for $9.99', '<p> Today (1/12) only! GNC is offering select MultiVitamins for<strong> $9.99</strong>. Plus get a free Oxyelite Pro Trial Size (a $8 value) and free shipping with ANY order.</p>', 7, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(455, '2012-01-16 05:10:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210561867.jpg', 'http://www.clinique.com/linkshare.tmpl?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-exp-_-null-_-null&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-5T0jT.wDSivdWJ9Eab2TgQ&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clinique.com%2Fcheckout%2Fsamples.tmpl%3FLOCALE%3Den%5FUS%26show%5Fpromo%3D1', 'Clinique free shipping and three free bonus sample products w/ any order', '<p> Ending today (1/12)! Clinique is offering free shipping on any via coupon code &#8220;<strong>SKIN</strong>&#8220;. Plus, receive three free bonus sample products with any purchase. Choose from six extra sample products, such as fragrance, eye cream and makeup remover.</p>', 9, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(456, '2012-01-16 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210572777.jpg', 'http://www.clarinsusa.com', 'Clarins: 6-piece gift + three other samples + free shipping with $50 order', '<p> Clarins is offering  6-piece Gift with a $50 purchase via coupon code <strong>JANGIFT. </strong>You can get free shipping on any order via code<strong> &#8220;JANSHIP&#8221;</strong>. Plus receive three samples with any order<strong><br /> </strong></p>', 11, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(457, '2012-01-16 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210579484.jpg', 'http://www.urbandecay.com/sale/sale,default,sc.html', 'Urban Decay up to 90% off select beauty products', '<p> Urban Decay is cutting <strong>up to 90% off</strong> a selection of beauty products. Many items at the lowest price we could find. Shipping starts at $6. For example:</p> <ul> <li> Vintage Urban Defense Tinted Moisturizer with SPF 20 <strong>$3</strong></li> <li> Liquid Liner <strong>$5</strong></li> <li> Pocket Rocket Lip Gloss <strong>$5</strong></li> <li> More on sale items <strong><br /> </strong></li> </ul>', 6, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(458, '2012-01-16 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210573891.jpg', 'http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/linkshare.tmpl?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-exp-_-null-_-null&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-ZdGLzR7gut0euYTB3Xy_OQ&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bobbibrowncosmetics.com%2Ftemplates%2Fshoponline%2Findex.tmpl%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-null-_-null-_-null', 'Bobbi Brown: free two deluxe samples + another two samples + free shipping with any order', '<p> Bobbi Brown Cosmetics is offering free two deluxe samples (Extra Repair Serum 5ml &amp; Extra Eye Repair Cream 3ml) and free shipping with ANY order via code &#8220;<strong>EXTRA2</strong>&#8221; at checkout. Plus choose another two free samples at checkout.</p>', 19, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(459, '2012-01-16 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210573788.jpg', 'http://usa.loccitane.com/FO/Error.aspx?code=404&referer=/FO/Lucky-Bag,p937133.htm?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-User-_-Default-_-None', 'LOccitane Lucky Bag (a $98 value) for $45 + free shipping', '<p> L’Occitane is having the Lucky Bag for $45 (it is a $98 value) + free shipping . It includes Shea Vanilla Shower Cream 16.9 oz, Shea Soap Orange Honey 3.5 oz, Rose 4 Reines Bath &amp; Body Lotion 2.5 oz, and these mystery products: Two travel sized shower products, a travel sized moisturizer, a full size lip gloss, and a bath treat.</p>', 9, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(460, '2012-01-16 05:10:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210574768.jpg', 'http://www.walgreens.com/', 'Exergen Comfort Scanner Temporal Thermometer 2 Second Reading for $15', '<p> Walgreens is offering the Exergen Comfort Scanner Temporal Thermometer 2 Second Reading for $40 &#8211; $5 with code <strong>RMN5</strong> - $20 rebate = <strong>$15</strong> with free shipping.</p>', 4, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(461, '2012-01-16 05:10:58', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152210589036.jpg', 'http://www.perfumania.com/shop/christmas-bogo/?showAllProducts=true&pageSize=96&sort=price%2bdesc', 'Perfumania: buy one fragrance get a second fragrance for $9.99', '<p>Alive again! Perfumania offers buy one select fragrance and get a second fragrance of equal or lesser value for <strong>$9.99</strong>. (The discount is applied in cart.) Even better, all orders qualify for free shipping on order of $25 or more and receive three samples for free. Receive CURVE SOUL For Women .50 oz EDP/S Free Gift With $60 Purchase. Offer is valid through 12/12.</p> <p>For example: <strong>TWO </strong> GUCCI Eau De Parfum Spray (2.5oz) for<strong> $84</strong> compared and reviews at Macy&#8217;s (<strong>ONE </strong>for $100).</p>', 8, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(462, '2012-01-16 05:12:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152212154845.jpg', 'http://www.shoes.com/?partnerid=performics2', 'Shoes.com: Extra 25% off + Free Shipping on Select Sale Priced Shoes', '25% off after coupon 25SALE Free Shipping', 7, 'Fatwallet Clothing'),
(463, '2012-01-16 05:35:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152235435139.jpg', 'http://www.puritan.com/Default.asp?scid=4150&afid=63&safid=LNKSHR&siteid=Jv.v1_Wldzg-33ldbi5Pcod65CbGOWGPvQ', 'Buy 2 Get 3 Free and Extra 10% Off Puritan''s Pride Vitamin Sale', '<ul> <li> Puritan''s Pride offers to purchase two Puritan''s Pride brand vitamins or supplements and get three additional vitamins or supplements for <b>free</b>. </li> <li> Alternatively, buy one Puritan''s Pride brand vitamin or supplement and get a second vitamin or supplement for <strong>free</strong>. </li> <li>Use coupon code " TAP12CC " to get Extra 10% Off. </li> <li> Shipping costs $4.95, but orders over $75 receive free shipping. </li></ul>', 5, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(464, '2012-01-16 05:35:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152235438828.jpg', 'http://www.spalook.com/p-13887-jurlique-balance-dryness-kit.aspx?AID=10745948&PID=4097299&URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spalook.com%2Fp-13887-jurlique-balance-dryness-kit.aspx', '$32 Jurlique Balance Dryness Kit, A $65 Value', 'SpaLook offers Jurlique Balance Dryness Kit, A $65 Value &nbsp;for $32 via code NEW20', 7, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(465, '2012-01-16 05:38:51', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120115/201201152238512937.jpg', 'http://www.joesnewbalanceoutlet.com/detail.asp?style=MCN630BR', 'Dunham 630 Men''s Casual/Dress Shoes', '<li> One Day Only</li> <li> Shipping is $4.95 (choose UPS Basic Shipping Method). </li> <b>Dunham 630 Men''s Casual/Dress Shoes</b><br />This stylish casual shoe is designed for all day comfort and stability with an ABZORB® heel and forefoot plus the ROLLBAR® for enhanced motion control.<br /><br /> ROLLBAR® with Medial & Lateral TPU Posts for ultimate motion control<br /> ABZORB® cushioning in both heel and forefoot for exceptional shock absorption<br /> Fiberglass Stability Shank embedded into midsole supports the arch and helps create a smoother gait<br /> Waterproof Leather upper repels moisture to keep feet dry and comfortable<br /> Brushed nylon covered ABZORB® insert - washable and removable for convenience<br /> IMEVA (injection-molded EVA foam) midsole for firm yet flexible cushioning<br /> Non-marking TRU-TRAK® Soft Rubber Outsole features heel-to-toe water channel that directs water away from the contact surfaces of the outsole<br /> Top-loaded (direct contact) ABZORB® along full footbed provides superior shock absorption and ideal underfoot cushioning for maximum multi-mile comfort<br /> 360 degree Raw Hide Lace - provides better fit around the heel<br /> Color: Brown<br /> Weight: 12.9 oz.', 7, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
