(530, '2012-01-16 12:32:45', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201160532453550.jpg', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,540212,1930671', 'Vera Bradley: Buy one sale item, get the 2nd 50% off', 'At Vera Bradley , buy one sale item and get a second sale item for <strong>50% off</strong>. (You''ll see this discount in-cart.) That''s one of the best deals on sale items we''ve seen from Vera Bradley in recent months. Shipping is a flat <strong>$8</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $100 or more. Deal ends January 18.<p>A best bet is two Vera Bradley Mail Box Stationery Desk Sets in six colors (Buttercup pictured) for <strong>$33.75</strong> plus <strong>$8</strong> for shipping. That''s $20.88 per set and the lowest total price we could find. Each set includes 12 note cards, 12 stationery sheets, 12 postcards, 12 envelopes, two sticker sheets, and a decorative chest.</p>', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
