(578, '2012-01-16 22:37:22', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201161537227576.jpg', 'http://www.ewatches.com/cust/dailydealsteal.asp?utm_campaign=deals&utm_source=dealmoon&utm_medium=cpc&rid=dealmoon&PID=2165238', '$48.00 ($295,84% off) Rotary Women''s White Austrian Watch', '<ul><li>Today only (Jan 16), eWatches offers the Rotary Women''s White Austrian Watch , model no. LS42829/01, for <b>$48</b> with <b>free shipping</b>.</li><li><b>Features:</b> a stainless steel case, black leather strap, Japanese quartz movement, date display, water resistance to 330 feet, and more.</li></ul>', 4, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
