(580, '2012-01-16 22:44:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201161544062011.jpg', 'http://www.crocs.com/crocs-kids-hover-hi-top-metallic-sneak/11681%2Cdefault%2Cpd.html&siteID=7AJr1csao4Q-fs5.DyGTNnvkXsO_HxD8Ow', 'Crocs: up to 70% off winter sale + free shipping', '<p> Crocs is taking<strong> up to 70% off</strong> select styles for men, women, and kids as Winter Sale. (Final discount is applied in-cart.) Plus get free shipping on all orders via coupon code &#8220;<strong>FALLSHIP</strong>&#8220;. Note that get an <strong>extra $20 off</strong> orders of $100 or more via coupon code &#8220;<strong>JAN20</strong>&#8220;. Deal ends January 19. For example:</p> <ul> <li> Crocs Kids&#8217; Hover Sneak Hi Tops <strong>$14.99</strong></li> <li> Crocs Men&#8217;s Boundless Shoes <strong>$19.99</strong></li> <li> Crocs Men&#8217;s Crostrail Clogs <strong>$29.99</strong></li> <li> Crocs Women&#8217;s Crocband Winter Plaid Boots <strong>$39.99</strong></li> <li>See more deals at Crocs Winter Sale </li> </ul>', 5, 'Huaren Fashion'),
