(592, '2012-01-17 04:39:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201162139034751.jpg', 'http://www.rei.com/product/836089/the-north-face-etip-gloves-womens-2011-closeout?siteId=cjIsd2x-it3792&URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F836089&PID=2138476&AID=10547273&cm_mmc=CJ-_-Aff-_-2138476-_-10547273', 'The North Face Etip Gloves - Women''s', '<li> Today 01/16 Only!<li>Available in Deep Water (pictured) or TNF Black.</li> <li> Shipping is $5.99, or free shipping to your store. </li> Keep your hands warm while using your phone with The North Face Etip gloves! They let you make calls, surf the web and listen to your favorite tunes without taking your gloves off.<br /> X-static® fabric on tips of the index fingers and thumbs allows you to control your smart phone, digital music player or laptop mouse pad without removing the gloves<br /> Gloves are designed around 5 hand measurements for an accurate and consistent fit<br /> Polyester/elastane provides 4-way stretch and 3-season warmth; exterior has a smooth, durable face, and the interior is brushed for warmth and comfort<br /> The North Face Etip gloves have silicone grip patterns on the palms to keep gadgets from slipping out of your hand', 3, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(593, '2012-01-17 04:39:04', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201162139044469.jpg', 'http://www.kqzyfj.com/click-5467912-10812806', '7 For All Mankind Women''s  Double Knit Moto Jacket w/ Waffle Lapel', '<li> FREE SHIPPING </li> <li> Tax in KY, NC, NV, NY. </li> 7 For All Mankind Women''s Size Guide<br />Dress to kill in a little black jacket from 7 For All Mankind.<br />Cropped moto jacket in sleek stretch double knit.<br />Waffle knit collar and lapel provide textural contrast.<br />Open front.<br />Button cuff on the long sleeves.<br />Seamed back.<br />Button and tab accents on the back hem.<br />70% viscose, 27% polyamide, 3% spandex;<br />Trim: 97% polyamide, 3% elastane.<br />Dry clean only.<br />Imported.', 14, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(594, '2012-01-17 04:44:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201162144038821.jpg', 'http://shop.timberland.com/category/index.jsp?categoryId=3976199', 'Timberland an extra 30% off all sale items + extra 20% off coupon + Free Shipping', '<p> Timberland is offering <strong>an extra 30% off</strong> all sale items (see final price in cart). Even better, today (1/16) only, get extra 20% off with coupon code &#8220;SNOWFLAKE&#8221;. Free shipping with any order.</p>', 7, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(595, '2012-01-17 04:44:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201162144038465.jpg', 'http://www.finishline.com/store/shop/sale/mens-sale-shoes/reebok/_/N-1sb9pZ2z7gwZ1z141xm/Nf-P_SalePercent|GTEQ+30/Ns-P_SalePrice?categoryId=cat20065&pageTitle=Clearance&sourceid=affiliate&cid=k100947&lid=j5617196k100947', 'Finish Line: select Reebok Shoes on sale', '<p> Finish Line is offering select Reebok Shoes on sale. Men&#8217;s , Women&#8217;s and Girl&#8217;s are from <strong>$17.49</strong> and Boy&#8217;s are from <strong>$14</strong>. Shipping is $8, or choose ship to store to save on shipping. Even better, get $10 off $60 code: <strong>5YUEHIR5VT</strong>; or $20 off $100 code: <strong>3UFTW5I4N1</strong></p>', 59, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(596, '2012-01-17 05:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120116/201201162202412652.jpg', 'http://www.mchrono.com/SKUSearch.asp?scriteria=WM05137', 'Casio Men''s Edifice Solar Multi-Band Atomic Watch for $335 + free shipping', 'Today only, MChrono offers the Casio Men''s Edifice Solar Multi-Band Atomic Watch , model no. EQWM1100DC-1A2, to <b>$335</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $165. It features multi-band atomic timekeeping, solar rechargeable battery, date display, alarm, water resistance to 330 feet, and more.', 2, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
