(681, '2012-01-17 12:08:59', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170508595621.gif', 'http://www.lanebryant.com/?mcid=AFF&sid=AFFLBxk111512', 'Lane Bryant Coupon: 20% off Entire Order Online, $25 off $75, $50 off $150 or $75 off $225 Online &amp; In-store', 'Available Lane Bryant Coupons and Lane Bryant Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>20% off Entire Order</b> [Exp. 01/28]<br />Use Lane Bryant Coupon Code TY17CA <br /><li><b>$25 off $75, $50 off $150 or $75 off $225 or more</b> [Exp. 01/31]<br />* Online: Use Lane Bryant Coupon Code JANGCLB <br />* In-store: In-store Printable Lane Bryant Coupon', 3, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(682, '2012-01-17 12:33:39', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170533391157.png', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,540615,1932672', 'Converse Clearance Sale: Extra 25% off', 'Converse takes an <b>extra 25% off</b> Converse men''s, women''s, and kids'' shoes in its clearance section . (The discount shows in-cart.) That''s the largest discount we''ve seen from Converse on clearance items in almost a year. Shipping adds <strong>$5.95</strong> and sales tax is added where applicable. Deal ends January 22.<p>A best bet are these Chuck Taylor Vintage Slip Shoes in White (pictured) for the in-cart price of <strong>$44.99</strong> plus <strong>$5.95</strong> for shipping. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $19. They''re available in men''s sizes 12 and 13.5, or women''s sizes 13.5 and 15.</p><p>Note that the Converse site may be slow to load.</p>', 5, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(683, '2012-01-17 12:37:28', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170537281724.jpg', 'http://www.sharkstores.com/Shades?data1=VHhRVVB3b0JDeDBBQUJVY29UZ0FBQUhU&a_aid=8', '$5 axcess/men by Claiborne Men''s Airman Aviator Sunglasses', 'Today only (Jan 16), SharkStores offers the axcess/men by Claiborne Men''s Airman Aviator Sunglasses in Gunmetal for <strong>$5</strong> plus <strong >$2.95</strong> for shipping.', 4, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(684, '2012-01-17 13:37:26', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170637264054.png', 'http://www.overstock.com/Clothing-Shoes/Eddie-Domani-Mens-3-button-Suit/5115960/product.html?cid=209801&fp=F&TRACK=CSEShopzilla&mr:referralID=495e304e-40c9-11e1-b7d1-001b2166c62d&AID=10654383&PID=2165238&SID=no_refer', '$62.99 ($71.5,12% off) Eddie Domani Men''s 3-Button Suit', 'Overstock offers the Eddie Domani Men''s 3-Button Suit in Grey or Black for <b>$62.99</b> plus <strong >$2.95</strong> for shipping.', 3, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(685, '2012-01-17 13:44:27', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170644278267.jpg', 'http://www1.macys.com/shop/juniors?id=16904&LinkshareID=7AJr1csao4Q-VmUmIy8MPVG7v71DAveBnQ', 'Macys up to 75% off select womens junior coats + extra 15% off', '<p> Macy&#8217;s is cutting<strong> up to to 75% off</strong> select women&#8217;s junior coats + apply coupon code &#8220;<strong>SUPER</strong>&#8221; knocks an additional <strong>15% off</strong>. Shipping starts at $8 or spend $99 or more to qualify for free shipping.</p>', 3, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(686, '2012-01-17 14:02:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170702361381.png', 'http://www.fractionprice.com/detail.asp?utm_campaign=deals&utm_source=dealnews&utm_medium=cpc&rid=dealnews&bo_products_variance_id=108208', 'Red Line Men''s Traction Series Watch for $55 + free shipping', 'Today only, FractionPrice offers the Red Line Men''s Traction Series Watch , model no. 50026-02, for <b>$55</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s $7 under our September mention in this color and the lowest total price we could find by $12. It features a stainless steel case, silicone strap, Japanese quartz movement, water resistance to 330 feet, and more.', 7, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(687, '2012-01-17 14:02:37', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170702373141.jpg', 'http://www.swarovski-crystallized.com/store/uk/', 'Swarovski sale: Up to 70% off select jewelry and accessories', 'Swarovski takes <strong>up to 70% off</strong> select jewelry and accessories. That''s the best discount we''ve ever seen from Swarvoski, famous for crystal glass and related products. Shipping starts at <strong>$6.95</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $95 or more. Sale ends January 31.', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(688, '2012-01-17 14:02:37', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170702378203.jpg', 'http://www.josbank.com:80/menswear/shop/ProductDisplayView?storeId=11001&productId=256471&catalogId=10050&ddkey=http:JABOrderStatus', 'Jos. A. Bank Men''s Short Sleeve Polos for $25 each + $6 s&h', 'Today only, Jos. A. Bank offers a selection of its Jos. A. Bank Men''s Short Sleeve Polos for <strong>$24.97</strong> each. Shipping starts at <strong>$5.95</strong>, but all orders of $195 or more bag free shipping. That''s among the lowest total prices we''ve seen for these items, although we saw similar sweaters for $5 less last week (since expired). Sales tax is added where applicable.<p>A best bet is the Jos. A. Bank Men''s Traveler Striped Short Sleeve Polo (pictured) for <strong>$24.97</strong> plus <strong>$5.95</strong> for shipping. That''s $55 off and the lowest total price we could find, although we saw a similar polo for $3 less during Black Friday week. It''s available in sizes S through XXL.</p>', 6, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(689, '2012-01-17 14:39:04', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170739044665.gif', 'http://piperlime.gap.com/?tid=plaff2138476&ap=2&siteID=plafcid54', 'Piperlime Coupons: 20% off Entire Order + Free Shipping', '<li> FREE SHIPPING. </li> Available Piperlime Coupons and Piperlime Coupon Codes:<br /><li> 20% off Entire Order [Exp. 01/19]<br />Use Piperlime Coupon NEWYOU <br /><li> Free shipping on all Piperlime orders', 8, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(690, '2012-01-17 15:02:40', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170802406085.jpg', 'http://usa.tommy.com/tommy/?cid=aff:gan', 'Tommy Hilfiger: 50% off sale items + extra 15% off coupon', 'Tommy Hilfiger cuts an <strong>extra 50% off</strong> all sale items. (Discount is taken in-cart.) Even better, coupon code "WINTERTH15" takes an <strong>additional 15% off</strong> your entire order with no minimum purchase required. That''s tied with our mention from a week ago as the best stacking discount we''ve seen from Tommy Hilfiger since July, when we saw 50% off sale items plus an extra 20% off orders of $125 or more. Shipping starts at <strong>$7.95</strong>, but orders over $150 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable.', 5, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(691, '2012-01-17 15:10:55', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170810555295.jpg', 'http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/this-week-offers/', 'Shu Uemura free shipping on ANY order + deluxe samples', '<p> Ending today (1/15)! Shu Uemura is offering free shipping on ANY order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>FSHIPPING</strong>&#8220;. Plus select deluxe samples at checkout with any order.</p>', 5, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(692, '2012-01-17 15:32:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170832362348.jpg', 'http://www.botachtactical.com/ri80waplbo.html', 'Ridge Men''s Waterproof Boots for $40 + free shipping', 'Botach Tactical offers the Ridge Men''s Waterproof Boots in Black, model no. 8066, for <b>$39.98</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $95. They''re available in sizes 4 to 15, many in both medium and wide widths.', 2, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(693, '2012-01-17 15:32:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170832368176.jpg', 'http://www.monarchycollection.com/Nagasaki-Slim-Fit-p/m604180310421.htm', 'MNRKY Final Clearance Sale: All items for $10 each + $8 s&h', 'MNRKY cuts everything sitewide to <strong>$9.99</strong> each during its Final Clearance Sale . Shipping starts at <strong>$8</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $150 or more. That''s tied with our October mention as the best sale we''ve seen from MNRKY, which sells men''s apparel.<p>A best bet are the MNRKY Men''s Nagasaki Slim Fit Jeans in Rinse (pictured) for <strong>$9.99</strong> plus <strong>$8</strong> for shipping. That''s $155 off and the lowest total price we could find. They''re available in most sizes 36 to 42.</p>', 5, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(694, '2012-01-17 15:32:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201170832366479.png', 'http://gan.doubleclick.net/gan_click?mid=VHhXVWRRb0JDeHNBQUVXTHVjY0FBQU9k&lid=41000000001259428&pubid=21000000000054384&adurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ae.com%2Fweb%2Fbrowse%2Fproduct.jsp%3FcatId%3Dcat10007%26productId%3D2101_9366%26cid%3DAEO_CSE_K65590%26mr%3AreferralID%3D2f657757-411a-11e1-a1f9-001b2166c2c0', 'American Eagle: Extra 40% off clearance + 20% off + free shipping', 'Ending today, American Eagle Outfitters takes an <strong>extra 40% off</strong> clearance items. (Discount is applied in-cart.) Plus, coupon code "36892051" cuts an <strong>additional 20% off</strong>. Even better, all orders receive <b>free shipping</b>. All together, that''s among the best discounts we''ve seen from American Eagle in recent weeks. (We saw the same deal last week, but without free shipping.) Sales tax is added where applicable. Some best bets:<ul><li> AE Men''s NYC Fleece Hoodie for <b>$14.39</b></li><li> AE Women''s Striped Dolman Sweater for <b>$14.39</b></li><li> AE Women''s Asymmetric Jacket for <b>$28.79</b></li><li> AE Men''s Utility Parka (pictured) for <b>$95.99</b></li><li>browse all clearance items at American Eagle Outfitters </li></ul>', 6, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
