(740, '2012-01-18 01:11:00', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201171811007629.jpg', 'http://www.bergdorfgoodman.com/store/catalog/templates/silo.jhtml?itemId=cat000005&ecid=BGALRTnL5HPStwNw', 'Bergdorf Goodman Beauty Event', '<p> <strong>Bergdorf Goodman</strong> is having a <strong>Rewarding Beauty Event</strong> . Spend $200 on beauty to receive a cosmetic bag with eleven deluxe samples. There are over 40 GWPs during this event. Free Shipping with any order with code <strong>BTYBAG</strong>.</p>', 7, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(741, '2012-01-18 02:02:40', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201171902407536.jpg', 'http://www.lordandtaylor.com/?utm_source=GAN&utm_medium=Affiliates&utm_campaign=dealnews&utm_content=Ban&utm_term=na&cm_mmc=Affiliate-_-GAN-_-dealnews-_-Primary&tag=GAN&ctcampaign=221', 'Lord &amp; Taylor Winter Sale: Up to 60% off + extra 20% off', 'Ending today, Lord and Taylor takes <strong>up to 60% off</strong> select items during its One Great Winter Sale . Plus, coupon code &quot;SALE&quot; cuts an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> sitewide. That''s among the best percent-off discounts we''ve seen from this merchant in recent months, although we saw up to 80% off clearance items plus an extra 25% off last week (since expired). Shipping starts at <strong>$5.95</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $99 or more. Sales tax is added where applicable and some exclusions apply.<p>Of note, in-store shoppers can get a 20% off discount via this printable coupon .</p>', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(747, '2012-01-18 03:02:32', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172002328783.jpg', 'http://www.pennywise.biz', '6 Pairs of Puma Men''s Sports Casual Socks for $9 + 1-cent s&h', 'Until January 18 at 9 pm ET, Pennywise offers Six Pairs of Puma Men''s Sports Casual Socks for $9.99. Coupon code "DealForGirl1" cuts them to <strong>$8.99</strong>. With <strong>one cent</strong> for shipping, that''s $9 off and the lowest total price we could find. These socks come in one size, which fit men''s sizes 6 to 12.5.', 12, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(744, '2012-01-18 02:32:39', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201171932393207.png', 'http://www.meritline.com/fashion-alloy-watch-black---p-52588.aspx?clickid=VHhZdklnb0JDeG9BQUdMQW1AZ0FBQUV6&source=dealnews', 'Japanese Multicolor LED Watch for $7 + free shipping', 'Meritline offers this Japanese Multicolor LED Watch for <b>$6.99</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s $1 off list, tied with our August mention, and the lowest total price we''ve seen for this watch.<p>Expect this item to take two to three weeks to arrive.</p>', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(746, '2012-01-18 02:44:24', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201171944244446.jpg', 'http://www.dickssportinggoods.com/home/index.jsp', 'Dicks Sporting Goods: extra 25% off select clearance items', '<p> Dick&#8217;s Sporting Goods is offering an <strong>extra 25% off</strong> select clearance items . (note that eligible items are marked and discount is reflected in cart.) Shipping starts around $6.99 or get free shipping on orders of $49 or more. Footwear and other select apparel also qualify for free shipping with no minimum required.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(748, '2012-01-18 03:09:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172009038321.gif', 'http://www.kingsizedirect.com/?affiliate_id=008&affiliate_location_id=01&WT.mc_id=k111512&mid=j17408994k111512', 'King Size Direct Coupons: 40% off highest priced item, More', 'Available King Size Direct Coupons and King Size Direct Coupon Codes: <br /><li><b>40% off highest priced item</b> [Exp. 01/21/12]<br />Use King Size Direct Coupon Code KSBU40 <br /><li><b>10% off your order</b> [Exp. 02/20]<br />Use King Size Direct Coupon KSBT10 <br /><li><b>20% off $85 or more</b> [Exp. 03/31]<br />Use King Size Direct Coupon KS23617 <br /><li><b>Free Standard + Free Express Shipping on $25 or more</b> [Exp. 02/20]<br />Use King Size Direct Coupon KSBUX25', 18, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
