(761, '2012-01-18 05:06:05', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172206051817.png', 'http://www.walmart.com/ip/Taylor-57444012-Body-Fat-Monitor-Bath-Scale/14954872?wmlspartner=Jv*v1/Wldzg&sourceid=27914385502723460293&wmlspartner=NKa3hZyYoHA&sourceid=04984798864037453409', '$18.00 ($29.99,40% off) Taylor Body Fat Monitor Bath Scale', 'Walmart offers the Taylor Body Fat Monitor Bath Scale , model no. 57444012, for <strong>$18</strong> with <strong >97 cents</strong> for shipping.', 18, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(762, '2012-01-18 05:06:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172206065179.jpg', 'http://www.saksfifthavenue.com/main/WorldOfDesigner.jsp?FOLDER<>folder_id=2534374306388344&PRODUCT<>prd_id=845524446454076&bmUID=jj3iPT2&site_refer=AFF001&siteID=Jv.v1_Wldzg-ZOeu_yQj3vMfi51qbCUNtw&LScreativeid=1&LSlinkid=10&LSoid=243401&LSsid=Jv*v1/Wldzg', 'SUPER HOT! TWO Free 8-pc Gift ($151 value)Lancome Gift with Purchase @ Saks', '<strong >SUPER HOT!</strong> Update : If you input&nbsp; LANCOME4A ,&nbsp; LANCOME4B&nbsp; separately , &nbsp;you will get <strong >&nbsp;</strong><strong >TWO 8-pc gifts</strong><strong >!</strong> &nbsp; That''s super hot! At Saks, through January 29 or while supplies last with any $65 Lancome purchase you can choose a free eight piece gift valued at $151 : <ul><li>Visionnaire Serum</li><li>Absolue Premium Bx Creme SPF 15</li><li>La Base Pro Perfecting Makeup Primer</li><li>Hypnose Doll Lashes Mascara</li><li>Bi-Facil</li><li>Exclusive cosmetic bag&nbsp;designed by Sophie Theallet</li><li>For the <strong>warm</strong> gift enter code <strong >LANCOME4A</strong>, includes&nbsp;Color Design Eye Shadow Quad in Honeymoon, Kitten Heel, Platform, and Madison Avenue plus L’Absolu Rouge Lipcolor in Voile De Rose</li><li>For the <strong>cool</strong> gift enter code <strong >LANCOME4B</strong>, includes Color Design Eye Shadow Quad in Pink Pearls, Lavendar Girl, Clock Strikes 12, and Sultry Mauve plus L’Absolu Rouge Lipcolor in Fleur De Lis</li></ul>', 26, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(763, '2012-01-18 05:07:00', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172207005707.jpg', 'http://www.mchrono.com/SKUSearch.asp?scriteria=WM02432&clickid=0004b6c66845e7150a4232025ff96ec8', '$138.99 ($200,31% off) Casio Men''s Edifice Black Chronograph Watch', 'MChrono offers this Casio Men''s Edifice Black Collection Chronograph Watch , model no. EFA131BK-1AV, for <strong>$138.99</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>.', 16, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(764, '2012-01-18 05:08:53', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172208539734.jpg', 'http://us.levi.com/home/index.jsp', 'Levis Coupon: Free Shipping any Order, 10% off Any Order + Free Shipping on $50', '<li> Free Shipping on $50 </li> Levis Coupons and Available Levi''s Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>10% off Any Order</b> [Exp. 01/23/12]<br />Use Levi''s Coupon ANFS12L or CTPK11R <br /><li> Free shipping any order (Click to activate) <br /><li> Sign up for email updates and Receive Free Shipping', 16, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(765, '2012-01-18 05:11:07', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211071581.jpg', 'http://shop.elizabetharden.com/family/index.jsp?categoryId=2779912', 'Elizabeth Arden Gift with Purchase', '<p> <strong> </strong> Elizabeth Arden is having a after Holiday Cyber Beauty Buys event with up to 35% off + free shipping on $40 or more. Plus, you can combine the following percent coupon or Gift with Purchase promotions.</p> <ul> <li>With any $40 purchase receive free shipping and choose a free skincare gift. Enter one of these codes at checkout: <strong>CERAMIDE5</strong>, <strong>PREVAGE3</strong>, <strong>EIGHTHOUR4</strong>, or <strong>INTERVENE4</strong>.</li> <li>8-Piece best of beauty gift + free shipping with $40 order via code &#8220;<strong>8DEAL</strong>&#8220;</li> <li>20% off entire order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>NEWYEARS20</strong>&#8220;</li> <li> 15-Piece Luxe Collection for $29.5 with any Elizabeth Arden Purchase </li> <li> Free 8-Piece Deluxe Gift + FREE Shipping with ANY $40 order with code <strong>8WONDERS</strong></li> </ul> <p>Note that you can add 33-Piece Holiday Color Collection ($350 value) Just $45 with ANY $27.50 purchase.<strong> </strong>Note that you may combine this offer with above codes to maximize your purchase.<strong><br /> </strong></p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(766, '2012-01-18 05:11:07', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211072961.jpg', 'http://www.drugstore.com/templates/browse/content.asp?catid=112291&aid=333840&aparam=7AJr1csao4Q-QNO2D_9q7lSqo1BNmMB7Aw', 'Beauty.com: Red Carpet Ready set ($185 value) with $150 purchase', '<p> Beauty.com is offering a new Gift With Purchase : get Red Carpet Ready set which includes a black lace bag designed by Marchesa filled with these 17 deluxe samples (total value is over $185) with<strong> </strong> any <strong>$150</strong> Beauty.com purchase.</p>', 19, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(767, '2012-01-18 05:11:08', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211088038.jpg', 'http://www.thebodyshop-usa.com/linkshare.aspx?siteID=7AJr1csao4Q-B0IhhUdFpTlXKVP6A.O70Q&url=http://www.thebodyshop-usa.com/home-fragrance/home-fragrance-oils/spiced-vanilla-home-fragrance-oil.aspx?', 'The Body Shop: holiday scents 60% to 80% off + extra 10% off', '<p> The Body Shop is cutting<strong> 60% to 80% off</strong> select holiday scents, with prices starting at $1. Plus get another 10% off via coupon code &#8220;JOY10&#8243;. Member can save another 10%.  Get free shipping with any order sitewide. For example:</p> <ul> <li> The Body Shop Spiced Vanilla Home Fragrance Oil for <strong>$2</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Cranberry Joy Bubble Bath for <strong>$3</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Candied Ginger Body Scrub for <strong>$4</strong></li> <li> The Body Shop Candied Ginger Body Butter for <strong>$5</strong></li> <li>see all discounted holiday scents at The Body Shop </li> </ul>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(768, '2012-01-18 05:11:11', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211111367.jpg', 'http://www.gnc.com/family/index.jsp?categoryId=4127856&ab=CMS:HOMEPAGE:CMS:G1', 'GNC select Vitamins for $9.99', '<p> Today (1/12) only! GNC is offering select MultiVitamins for<strong> $9.99</strong>. Plus get a free Oxyelite Pro Trial Size (a $8 value) and free shipping with ANY order.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(769, '2012-01-18 05:11:11', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211115991.jpg', 'http://www.clinique.com/linkshare.tmpl?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-exp-_-null-_-null&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-cAsNqA0mjifmysV8aRx00g&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clinique.com%2Fcheckout%2Fsamples.tmpl%3FLOCALE%3Den%5FUS%26show%5Fpromo%3D1', 'Clinique free shipping and three free bonus sample products w/ any order', '<p> Ending today (1/12)! Clinique is offering free shipping on any via coupon code &#8220;<strong>SKIN</strong>&#8220;. Plus, receive three free bonus sample products with any purchase. Choose from six extra sample products, such as fragrance, eye cream and makeup remover.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(770, '2012-01-18 05:11:14', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211148504.jpg', 'http://www.clarinsusa.com', 'Clarins: 6-piece gift + three other samples + free shipping with $50 order', '<p> Clarins is offering  6-piece Gift with a $50 purchase via coupon code <strong>JANGIFT. </strong>You can get free shipping on any order via code<strong> &#8220;JANSHIP&#8221;</strong>. Plus receive three samples with any order<strong><br /> </strong></p>', 23, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(771, '2012-01-18 05:11:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211154602.jpg', 'http://www.urbandecay.com/sale/sale,default,sc.html', 'Urban Decay up to 90% off select beauty products', '<p> Urban Decay is cutting <strong>up to 90% off</strong> a selection of beauty products. Many items at the lowest price we could find. Shipping starts at $6. For example:</p> <ul> <li> Vintage Urban Defense Tinted Moisturizer with SPF 20 <strong>$3</strong></li> <li> Liquid Liner <strong>$5</strong></li> <li> Pocket Rocket Lip Gloss <strong>$5</strong></li> <li> More on sale items <strong><br /> </strong></li> </ul>', 22, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(772, '2012-01-18 05:11:18', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211182018.jpg', 'http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/linkshare.tmpl?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-exp-_-null-_-null&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-znbh0.261r7tvgVluTpw4Q&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bobbibrowncosmetics.com%2Ftemplates%2Fshoponline%2Findex.tmpl%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-null-_-null-_-null', 'Bobbi Brown: free two deluxe samples + another two samples + free shipping with any order', '<p> Bobbi Brown Cosmetics is offering free two deluxe samples (Extra Repair Serum 5ml &amp; Extra Eye Repair Cream 3ml) and free shipping with ANY order via code &#8220;<strong>EXTRA2</strong>&#8221; at checkout. Plus choose another two free samples at checkout.</p>', 65, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(773, '2012-01-18 05:11:18', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120117/201201172211188200.jpg', 'http://usa.loccitane.com/FO/Error.aspx?code=404&referer=/FO/Lucky-Bag,p937133.htm?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-User-_-Default-_-None', 'LOccitane Lucky Bag (a $98 value) for $45 + free shipping', '<p> L’Occitane is having the Lucky Bag for $45 (it is a $98 value) + free shipping . It includes Shea Vanilla Shower Cream 16.9 oz, Shea Soap Orange Honey 3.5 oz, Rose 4 Reines Bath &amp; Body Lotion 2.5 oz, and these mystery products: Two travel sized shower products, a travel sized moisturizer, a full size lip gloss, and a bath treat.</p>', 22, 'Huaren Beauty'),
