(815, '2012-01-18 07:06:22', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180006221041.jpg', 'http://www.lancome-usa.com/gift/gwp-2012-spring,default,pg.html?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-JanGWPOffer-_-SpringGWP&clickID=&pubID=BPBrrD0Gs3E', 'Free Gift ($122 value) Lancome 7 Free Samples with purchase of $75 or more', '<ul><li>Receive the exclusive 7-piece Lancôme.com Spring Gift when you spend $75 or more.&nbsp;</li><li> You can choose &nbsp;your favorite eye cream &amp; day moisturizer&nbsp; &amp; receive your 4 beauty essentials. </li><li> Offer Valid 1.14-1.22.12 </li></ul>', 19, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(816, '2012-01-18 07:07:22', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180007227695.jpg', 'http://www.journelle.com/our-favorites?clickid=0004b6c814c0976a0a4286a3604907da', '50%-70% Off Sale + Extra 10% Off at Journelle.com', '<ul><li> Journelle.com has 50-70% off sale on Designer Lingeries , starting from 1/17 </li><li> Use our exclusive coupon code&nbsp; DealForGirl &nbsp;&nbsp;to get extra 10% off! </li><li> Free shipping over $100, or free pick up in store (Locations in New York &amp; Miami) </li></ul>', 26, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(817, '2012-01-18 07:32:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180032571987.png', 'http://www.kohls.com/kohlsStore/clearance.jsp', 'Kohl''s Gold Star Clearance: 60% to 80% off + extra 20% off', 'Kohl''s cuts <strong>60% to 80% off</strong> items in its Gold Star Clearance . Plus, coupon code &quot;SMS9999&quot; takes an <strong>extra 20% off</strong>. That''s among the biggest percent-off discounts we''ve seen from Kohl''s in recent weeks. (We saw outerwear for 60% off plus an extra 20% off earlier today.) Shipping starts at <strong>$5.95</strong>, but orders over $75 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable. Coupon expires January 21.<p>A best bet is the Arrow Men''s Striped Milano Sweater in Stonedust, Fudge, or Black for <strong>$9.60</strong> after the above coupon. With <strong>$5.95</strong> for shipping, that''s $50 off and the lowest total price we could find. It''s available in sizes S, L, XL, and XXL, although not in all size/color combinations.</p>', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(828, '2012-01-18 09:08:59', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180208593077.gif', 'http://www.stevemadden.com/?utm_source=cj&utm_medium=affiliate&affSource=CJ&utm_campaign=2011&omid=affiliate&CID=cj_2138476', 'Steve Madden Coupons: 15% off Entire Order + Free Shipping', 'Available Steve Madden Coupons and Steve Madden Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>15% off any order + free shipping</b><br />Use Steve Madden Coupon Steve15 <br /><li><b>15% off $75 + Free Shipping</b> [Exp. 02/29]<br />Use Steve Madden Coupon Code WINTER15 <br /><li><b>Free Shipping on any order</b><br />Use Steve Madden Coupon Code HOLIDAY <br /><li><b>Free Shipping on $75 or More</b><br />Use Steve Madden Coupon Code SMFREESHIP <br />* Does not apply to clearance items<br /><li> Join the mailing list and save 10% on your next order <br />', 18, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(818, '2012-01-18 07:37:01', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180037017366.jpg', 'http://www.bathandbodyworks.com/product/index.jsp?productId=2257431&cm_mmc=Shopzilla-_-CSE-_-2257431-_-2766765&cp=4090263', '$16.00 ($40,60% off) 4 Tubes of C.O. Bigelow 5-oz. Shave Cream w/ Eucalyptus Oil', '<ul><li>Bath &amp; Body Works offers the C.O. Bigelow 5-oz. Premium Shave Cream with Eucalyptus Oil for $10. </li><li> add four tubes to your cart for $20.</li><li>Coupon code " GIFT20 " drops it to <strong>$16</strong> with <strong >$6.99</strong> for shipping. </li></ul>', 17, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
