(835, '2012-01-18 12:02:39', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180502395030.jpg', 'http://www.ashford.com/ashford/browse/productDetail.jsp?source=406555555&productId=0604230&categoryId=cat1130082', 'Movado Men''s Museum Watch for $249 + free shipping', 'Ashford offers the Movado Men''s Museum Watch , model no. 0604230, for <strong>$249</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s $301 off and the lowest total price we could find. It features a leather strap, stainless steel case, Swiss quartz movement, water resistance to 100 feet, and more.', 28, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(836, '2012-01-18 12:02:39', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180502392172.jpg', 'http://www.holabirdsports.com/cgi-bin/product?utm_medium=cpc&utm_source=dealnews&product=112356', 'adidas Men''s Barricade Team Shoes for $43 + $6 s&h', 'Today only, Holabird Sports offers the adidas Men''s Barricade Team Shoes in White/Black/Metallic Silver (pictured), White/Collegiate Royal/Light Onyx , or White/Metallic Silver/Black/Red for <strong>$42.95</strong> plus <strong>$5.75</strong> for shipping. That''s tied with our mention from a month ago and the lowest total price we could find by $7. They come in sizes 6.5 to 14, although not all size/color combinations are available.', 14, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(837, '2012-01-18 12:32:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180532487775.jpg', 'http://www.lanebryant.com/plus-size-sale-clothing-initmate-apparel/view-all-clearance/4053c18831/index.cat?intid=LB01712x0005&mcid=AFF&sid=AFFLBxk54384', 'Lane Bryant: Up to 70% off + extra 30% off', 'Lane Bryant knocks <strong>up to 70% off</strong> items in its Clearance section. Plus, take an <strong>extra 30% off</strong> via coupon code "000307697". That''s a 15% greater savings than our mention from last week and among the best percent-off discounts we''ve seen from Lane Bryant in recent months. Shipping starts at <b>$7.95</b>, or choose free ship-to-store. Sales tax is added where applicable. Deal ends January 20.', 12, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(838, '2012-01-18 12:44:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180544157112.jpg', 'http://www.neimanmarcus.com/index.jhtml?', 'Neiman Marcus Extra 25% off select sale items + free shipping', '<p> Today (1/16) only, Neiman Marcus offers an <strong>extra 25% off</strong> select sale items as Last Call Sale, discount appears in-cart. Even better, apply coupon code &#8220;JANFS&#8221; to get <strong>free shipping</strong>.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(839, '2012-01-18 13:05:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180605578341.jpg', 'http://www.sharkstores.com/For-Her?data1=VHhRd3pBb0JDeHdBQUI4QXFZNEFBQUdL&a_aid=8', '$9 3-Piece Bumpits Hair Volumizing Inserts 2-Pack', 'Today only (Jan 16), SharkStores offers 3-Piece Bumpits Hair Volumizing Inserts 2-Pack in Dark Brown / Black (pictured), Blonde, or Light Brown for <strong>$9</strong> plus $1.99 for shipping.', 14, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(840, '2012-01-18 13:37:28', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180637286547.jpg', 'http://www.overstock.com/Clothing-Shoes/DKNY-Womens-Quilted-Down-filled-Walking-Coat/6141468/product.html?TRACK=affcjfeed&PID=4328635&AID=10654383&CID=207442&fp=F&SID=no_refer', '$71.99 ($90.79,21% off) DKNY Women''s Quilted Down-filled Walking Coat', '<ul><li>Overstock.com offers DKNY Women''s Quilted Down-filled Walking Coat for $71.99 . </li><li>To get this deal: </li><ul><li><b> Click Here </b> and add to cart </li><li>Now activate 10% off coupon (New Customers) </li><li>Your final price will be $79.99 - 10% off =<b > $71.99 </b> + $2.95 Shipping </li></ul> </ul>', 13, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(841, '2012-01-18 14:10:59', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180710596930.jpg', 'http://www1.macys.com/shop/product/draper-7-piece-jacquard-comforter-sets?ID=593419&LinkshareID=7AJr1csao4Q-bz9VUOZSwwhs1ihJiNwhCQ', 'Draper 7 Piece Jacquard Comforter Sets for $70', '<p> Macys offers the Draper 7 Piece Jacquard Comforter Sets for $79.99 &#8211; $10 off $75+ order with Coupon <strong>XJW562A992 </strong>=<strong> $69.99</strong>. Free Shipping with $99 or more order.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(842, '2012-01-18 15:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180802419979.jpg', 'http://www.peterglenn.com/product/north-face-windstopper-ear-gear-headband-mens', 'Peter Glenn: Free shipping sitewide, stacks with sale', 'Peter Glenn offers <strong>free shipping</strong> on all orders with no minimum purchase required. That''s the best such shipping offer we''ve seen from this merchant, which usually requires a purchase of $49 or more for free shipping. Even better, it stacks with its Winter Sale , which cuts <b>up to 50% off</b> select items.<p>A best bet is The North Face Windstopper Ear Gear Headband in Black for <b>$16.99</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $9. It features Polartec fleece construction and is available in sizes M and L.</p>', 29, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(843, '2012-01-18 15:02:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180802427686.jpg', 'http://usa.tommy.com/tommy/?cid=aff:gan', 'Tommy Hilfiger coupon: 50% off sale items + extra 20% off', 'Tommy Hilfiger cuts an <strong>extra 50% off</strong> all sale items. (Discount is taken in-cart.) Even better, coupon code "THDEDICATED20" takes an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> with no minimum purchase required. That''s beats yesterday''s mention of an extra 15% off and is now the best stacking discount we''ve ever seen from Tommy Hilfiger. Shipping starts at <strong>$7.95</strong>, but orders over $150 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable. Coupon expires January 31.', 12, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(844, '2012-01-18 15:11:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120118/201201180811066415.jpg', 'http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/this-week-offers/', 'Shu Uemura free shipping on ANY order + deluxe samples', '<p> Ending today (1/15)! Shu Uemura is offering free shipping on ANY order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>FSHIPPING</strong>&#8220;. Plus select deluxe samples at checkout with any order.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Beauty');
