(1005, '2012-01-19 15:32:33', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190832334349.jpg', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,541608,1937039', 'Keen Women''s Bern Low Boots for $80 + free shipping', 'REI offers Keen Women''s Bern Low Boots in Oak (pictured), Black, or Oatmeal for <strong>$79.93</strong> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s tied with our mention from a week ago and lowest total price we could find by $70. Sales tax is added where applicable. They''re available in most sizes from 6 to 9, although not in all color/size combinations.', 22, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1006, '2012-01-19 15:32:33', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190832339230.jpg', 'http://www.stevemadden.com/Item.aspx?gid=16800&omid=cse&utm_source=shpg&utm_medium=cse&utm_campaign=2011&', 'Steve Madden: Up to 50% off clearance items', 'Steve Madden takes <strong>up to 50% off</strong> clearance items . (Discount is reflected on product page.) That''s ties last week''s mention as the best discount we''ve seen on clearance items since September when they took 50% off plus an extra 20% off. (We have seen sitewide discounts up to 30% off since then, but sale items are usually only marked up to 30% off initially.) Shipping adds <strong>$6.95</strong> or get free shipping on orders of $75 or more via coupon code "SMFREESHIP". Sales tax is added where applicable.<p>A best bet is the Steve Madden Men''s GAMMBLER Boots in Tan Leather (pictured), Dark Brown, or Black Leather for <strong>$64.98</strong> plus <strong>$6.95</strong> for shipping. That''s $6 under last week''s mention and the lowest total price we could find by $83. These shoes come in sizes ranging from 7 to 13, although not all size size/color combinations are available.</p>', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1007, '2012-01-19 15:32:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190832341601.png', 'http://www.lids.com/?AID=8828990&PID=552179&SID=VHhnM2RRb0JDeGtBQURvcHJETUFBQU1t&cpid=cj', 'Lids Blowout Sale: Hats, T-shirts, more for $5', 'Lids offers select hats, T-shirts, and more for <strong>$5</strong> each as part of its Blowout Sale . That''s tied with our mention from last week as one of the best sales we''ve seen from Lids on these items in recent months. (For further comparison, three weeks ago we saw a similar sale that applied to hats only but also included a buy one get a second for 50% off discount, since expired.) Shipping adds a flat-rate <strong>$4.99</strong>, or opt for free ship-to-store. (All orders over $50 get free shipping.) Sales tax is added where applicable.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1008, '2012-01-19 15:32:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190832344301.jpg', 'http://www.shopnewbalance.com//men/shoes/running/training/MR580WSB?s1=PriceGrabber&s2=DF&s3=MR580WSB', 'Shop New Balance Clearance: Up to 65% off + free shipping', 'Shop New Balance cuts <strong>up to 65% off</strong> select New Balance shoes and apparel during its Clearance Sale. Plus, activate <strong>free shipping</strong> via this link . That the best percent-off deal we''ve ever seen on clearance items at Shop New Balance. Deal ends January 23. Notables:<ul><li> New Balance Men''s 6017 Flip Flops for <b>$16.99</b></li><li> New Balance Men''s 580 Running Shoes (pictured) for <b>$34.99</b></li><li> New Balance Women''s 573 Running Shoes for <b>$37.99</b></li><li> New Balance Men''s 811 Walking Shoes for <b>$39.99</b></li><li> New Balance Women''s 1105 Walking Shoes for <b>$39.99</b></li><li>see all shoes and apparel on sale at Shop New Balance </li></ul>', 23, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1009, '2012-01-19 15:32:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190832352844.jpg', 'http://usa.tommy.com/tommy/browse/productDetailWithPicker.jsp?productId=RM87603557&utm_source=pricegrabber&utm_medium=cse&cid=cse:pg:RM87603557', 'Tommy Hilfiger Women''s Dipped Trench Coat for $44 + $8 s&h', 'Tommy Hilfiger offers the Tommy Hilfiger Women''s Dipped Trench Coat for $109.99. In-cart it drops to $55. Coupon code "THDEDICATED20" further cuts it to <strong>$44</strong>. With <strong>$7.95</strong> for shipping, that''s $57 off and the lowest total price we could find. Sales tax is added where applicable. It''s available in sizes M to XXL.', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1010, '2012-01-19 16:02:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190902342194.png', 'http://www.naturalizer.com/?partnerid=performics2', 'Naturalizer End of Season Sale: Up to 70% off + extra 15% off', 'Naturalizer knocks <strong>up to 70% off</strong> during its End of Season Sale . (Prices are as marked.) Plus, coupon code "NATLOVECC" cuts an <strong>additional 15% off</strong>. That ties last week''s mention and is among the best discounts we''ve seen from Naturalizer in recent months, although we saw up to 76% off plus 25% off with an extra 15% off and free shipping six weeks ago. Shipping starts at <b>$6.50</b>, or get free shipping on orders over $200. Sales tax is added where applicable and some exclusions apply.', 14, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1011, '2012-01-19 16:02:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190902351371.jpg', 'http://www.botachtactical.com/otb942mtn.html', 'New Balance OTB Men''s Bootistan Waterproof Boots for $90 + free shipping', 'Botach Tactical offers the New Balance OTB Men''s Bootistan Waterproof Boots for <b>$89.95</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s $106 off list and the lowest total price we could find. They''re available in sizes 6 to 15, and feature a 360&deg; rubber rand for protection against rocks, waterproof leather, waterproof Sympatex membrane, and Vibram rubber outsoles.', 36, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1012, '2012-01-19 16:10:59', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190910595669.jpg', 'http://www.shuuemura-usa.com/_us/_en/this-week-offers/', 'Shu Uemura free shipping on ANY order + deluxe samples', '<p> Ending today (1/15)! Shu Uemura is offering free shipping on ANY order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>FSHIPPING</strong>&#8220;. Plus select deluxe samples at checkout with any order.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(1013, '2012-01-19 16:12:16', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190912167999.jpg', 'http://www.graveyardmall.com/categories/Daily-Deal/', 'GraveyardMall.com: 6 Pairs of Boys or Girls Licensed Sunglasses', '$9.99 (was $48.00) Free Shipping', 13, 'Fatwallet Clothing'),
(1014, '2012-01-19 16:35:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190935447825.jpg', 'http://www.conair-store.com/index.asp', '15% OFF Conair Coupon: extra 15% off your purchase', 'Conair online store , which sells hair, bath, and personal grooming products, offers extra 15% off with coupon code:<strong> CONAIRSAVE15</strong> (Ends March 31).', 15, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(1015, '2012-01-19 16:37:11', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190937118957.png', 'http://www.josbank.com/menswear/shop/ProductDisplayView?storeId=11001&productId=263678&catalogId=10050&ddkey=http:ReferralView', '$29.97 ($165,82% off) Jos. A. Bank Men''s Dress Trousers', '<ul><li> Today only (Jan 18), Jos. A. Bank offers Jos. A. Bank Dress Trousers &nbsp;for only&nbsp;<strong>$29.97</strong>. </li><li> Shipping starts at $8.95, or spend $195 to get shipping for free. Some highlights: </li></ul> <ul><ul><li> Jos. A. Bank Men''s Executive Plaid Wool Pleated Trousers for <strong>$29.97</strong></li><li> Jos. A. Bank Men''s Executive Patterned Wool Pleated Trousers (pictured) for <strong>$29.97</strong></li><li> Jos. A. Bank Men''s Cotton Corduroy Pleated Front Dress Trousers for <strong>$29.97</strong></li></ul></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(1016, '2012-01-19 16:41:10', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120119/201201190941108016.jpg', 'http://www.perryellis.com/The-Private-Sale/peprivate,default,sc.html', 'Perry Ellis: Private Sale Collection Offer + an extra 50% off', '<p> Perry Ellis is having a Private Sale Collection Offer + <strong>an Extra 50% off </strong>with code <strong>PEPRIVATE</strong>.</p>', 22, 'Huaren Fashion'),
