(1181, '2012-01-20 17:32:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201032445325.jpg', 'http://www.backcountry.com/marmot-eclipse-softshell-jacket-womens.html?CMP_SKU=MAR1594&MER=0406&CMP_ID=SH_BZR001&mv_pc=r111&003=7163333&010=MAR1594-WAL-S&mr:referralID=af9d3e8c-438c-11e1-b2fa-001b2166becc', 'Marmot Women''s Eclipse Softshell Jacket for $63 + free shipping', 'Backcountry offers Marmot Women''s Eclipse Softshell Jacket in Walnut for <strong>$62.98</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $37. It available in sizes S and M.', 20, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
