(1186, '2012-01-20 18:02:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201102546041.png', 'http://www.meritline.com/zinc-aluminum-alloy-quartz-watch---p-52572.aspx?clickid=VHhtc0dnb0JDeHdBQUNGdm5wb0FBQVBC&source=dealnews', 'Zinc-Aluminum Alloy Quartz Watch for $5 + free shipping', 'Meritline offers this Zinc-Aluminum Alloy Quartz Watch for <strong>$4.99</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s $1 off list and the lowest total price we could find for this particular watch. It features a zinc-aluminum alloy case and quartz movement. Note that this watch is not water resistant.<p>Expect this item to take two to three weeks to arrive.</p>', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1187, '2012-01-20 18:02:55', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201102558936.jpg', 'http://store.americanapparel.net/', 'American Apparel coupon: free shipping no minimum', 'American Apparel offers <strong>free shipping</strong> sitewide with no minimum purchase required via coupon code "zeroshipping". It also stacks on sale items which start at <strong>$2</strong>. That''s tied with December''s mention as the best free shipping deal we''ve seen from American Apparel. Sales tax is added where applicable. Coupon expires January 22.', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
