(1196, '2012-01-20 20:32:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201332348701.jpg', 'http://www.eddiebauer.com/catalog/product.jsp?ensembleId=41080&oessoa=6046151&cm_mmc=CSE-_-Shopping_com-_-Women%27s%20Shoes_and_Accessories%7cShop%20by%20Brand%7cEddie%20Bauer-_-1038449', 'Eddie Bauer Clearance Sale: Extra 30% off + 20% off', 'Eddie Bauer still cuts an <strong>extra 30% off</strong> men''s and women''s clearance items . (The discount applies automatically in cart.) Plus, get <strong>20% off</strong> sitewide, with no minimum purchase required, via coupon code "BADCQ3411". Combined, that''s one of the best discounts we''ve seen from Eddie Bauer in recent months, although we saw a 30% off sitewide discount in early December. Shipping starts at <strong>$7.99</strong> and sales tax is added where applicable.<p>A best bet are the Eddie Bauer Women''s Down Faux-Fur Trim Boots in Gray (pictured) or Brown for $39.99. Add them to your cart and apply the above coupon to drop it to <strong>$22.39</strong>. With <strong>$7.99</strong> for shipping, that''s $18 off and the lowest total price we could find. It''s available sizes 6 to 12, although not in all size/color combinations.</p>', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
