(1199, '2012-01-20 21:02:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201402344293.jpg', 'http://www.ice.com/pendants/silver-pendant-prd_psy_102276.jsp?srccode=cii_13736960&cpncode=22-196808201-2', 'ICE.com: $20 off regularly-priced jewelry of $20 or more + free shipping', 'ICE.com takes <strong>$20 off</strong> most regularly-priced orders of $20 or more via coupon code "S20AU". Plus, all items qualify for <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the best dollar-off coupon we''ve seen from ICE.com since four weeks ago, when it took $25 off $25 or more. Note that sale items, clearance, engagement rings, and bridal rings are excluded from the discount.<p>A best bet is the 20mm Crystal Heart Pendant with Sterling Silver Chain (pictured), model no. PSY 102276, for $45. That drops to <strong>$25</strong> after coupon. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that''s $20 off list and the lowest total price we could find.</p>', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1200, '2012-01-20 21:05:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120120/201201201405424384.png', 'http://www.payless.com/store/?AID=10386949&PID=552179&SID=VHhYVlRBb0JDeGtBQURkdFJVc0FBQUJV&cm_ven=CJ&cm_ite=Logo+-+88x31&cm_pla=552179&cm_cat=551655', 'Extra 20% OFF Payless Sale: Buy 1 item, get 50% off 2nd + extra 20% off', '<ul><li>At Payless , buy one item and get <strong>50% off</strong> a second item . Plus, take an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> via coupon code " 42612 ". </li><li>Shipping is a flat <strong>$5.95</strong>. Ship-to-store is free.</li></ul>', 16, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
