(1366, '2012-01-21 22:03:09', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120121/201201211503093178.jpg', 'http://www.gandermountain.com/modperl/product/details.cgi?pdesc=Columbia_Mens_Hart_Mountain_II_Hoodie&i=442562&r=view&aID=501G3&cID=GSHOP_442562', 'Columbia Men''s Hart Mountain II Hoodie for $24 + free shipping', 'Gander Mountain offers the Columbia Men''s Hart Mountain II Hoodie in five colors (Red Element pictured) for <strong>$24.49</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $4. Sales tax is added where applicable. It''s available in M to XLT, though not in all size/color combinations.', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1367, '2012-01-21 22:05:45', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120121/201201211505458865.png', 'http://www.payless.com/store/?AID=10386949&PID=552179&SID=VHhYVlRBb0JDeGtBQURkdFJVc0FBQUJV&cm_ven=CJ&cm_ite=Logo+-+88x31&cm_pla=552179&cm_cat=551655', 'Extra 20% OFF Payless Sale: Buy 1 item, get 50% off 2nd + extra 20% off', '<ul><li>At Payless , buy one item and get <strong>50% off</strong> a second item . Plus, take an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> via coupon code " 42612 ". </li><li>Shipping is a flat <strong>$5.95</strong>. Ship-to-store is free.</li></ul>', 25, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
