(1370, '2012-01-21 23:03:05', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120121/201201211603052398.jpg', 'http://www.forever21.com/Product/Category.aspx?br=f21&category=sale', 'Forever 21 Clearance Sale: Deals from $2 + $6 s&h', 'Forever 21 discounts over 800 items as part of its Clearance Sale . Shipping adds <strong>$5.95</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $50 or more. That''s one of the better sales we''ve seen from Forever 21 in recent months, though we saw similar prices with free shipping with no minimum in early December. Sales tax is added where applicable. Accessories start at <strong>$1.99</strong>, bras from <strong>$3.99</strong>, shorts from <strong>$3.99</strong>, and tops from <strong>$4.99</strong>.', 23, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1371, '2012-01-21 23:03:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120121/201201211603065226.jpg', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,542287,1939925', 'Sears Winter Clearance Sale: Up to 60% off + extra 30% off', 'Sears takes <strong>up to 60% off</strong> clearance items as part of its Winter Clearance Sale . Even better, coupon code "SEARS30" takes an <strong>extra 30% off</strong>. Shipping starts around <strong>$5</strong>, although free shipping is offered on select items. That''s the best deal we''ve seen on many of these items from Sears since October, when it took up to 90% off. Sales tax is added where applicable. Deal ends January 26.<p>A best bet are these Levi''s Junior''s Twill Skinny Pants in Green for $29.99 before coupon, <strong>$20.99</strong> after. With <strong>$5.55</strong> shipping, That''s $21 off list and the lowest total price we could find. They''re available in sizes 3 to 13.</p>', 24, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
