(1449, '2012-01-22 09:05:46', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120122/201201220205464404.jpg', 'http://www.ulta.com/ulta/browse/productDetail.jsp?productId=xlsImpprod4080011', 'Free 7-pc Elizabeth Arden Gift Gift ($75 value) Ulta Gift With Purchase', '<ul><li>Today only (Jan 12) at Ulta <strong></strong>, with any $35 purchase from any brand you will&nbsp;receive a free <strong>seven piece Elizabeth Arden bonus</strong> (a $75 value), includes: </li><ul><li>Ceramide Plump Perfect Ultra Lift and Firm Moisture Cream SPF 30, </li><li>Intervene 3-in-1 Daily Cleanser Exfoliator Primer, </li><li>Prevage Serum, </li><li>Pretty EDP deluxe mini, </li><li>a Red Door keepsake mirror, </li><li>a full size Exceptional Lipstick in Amber, </li><li>a platinum ostrich-embossed tote</li></ul><li>No code&nbsp;is needed, just add the free gift to your cart before you check out. </li><li>Right now they have gifts with purchase from Philosophy,&nbsp;Dermalogica, and Benefit. </li><li>Shipping is free with a $25 purchase with code <strong>SHIPJAN12</strong> at checkout.</li></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
