(1451, '2012-01-22 09:10:55', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120122/201201220210557823.jpg', 'http://www.sephora.com/index.jhtml?om_mmc=aff-linkshare-homepage-piaqBdsdpmQ&_requestid=142591', 'Sephora 17 free samples or free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &#038; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 order', '<p> Sephora is offering a Skincare Sample Bag with 14 samples for free with orders of $25 or more via coupon code &#8220;<strong>TRY14</strong>&#8220;. Plus another three samples given with each order. Shipping starts at $5.95 or get free shipping with orders of $50 or more. The bag includes eye cream, moisturizer, serum, cleansing oil, day cream, and more. Note that you can also receive a free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 purchase via code <strong>LIPLOVE</strong> at checkout.</p>', 22, 'Huaren Beauty'),
