(1503, '2012-01-22 18:09:19', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120122/201201221109195465.jpg', 'http://www.tanga.com/products/golds-gym-mens-body-mapping-lifting-shirt', 'Gold''s Gym Men''s Body Mapping Lifting Shirt', '<li> Shipping is $4.99. </li> Playing sports and lifting weights will never be the same after you put on one of these bad boys.<br />The Golds Gym Powerlift Training Long Sleeve Shirt is designed with protective padding and grip zones making it ideal for weight training and sport equipment. Targeted compression supports key muscle groups and fights muscle fatigue. The non-slip sticky gel print keeps you stable on the bench while the built-in, reinforced padding cushions weights. Also great for protection under football and hockey pads!<br />In short, with all of the body mapping technology built in to this shirt you are sure to feel not a penny less than the newest version of the 6 million dollar man.<br />Check additional image for sizing chart.<br />*Order up to 3 units today for the same low shipping price of 3.99! *<br />Keep your eyes peeled and look to Tanga Accessories as your daily source for extreme value on fitness apparel, jewelry, sunglasses, watches, and much more!', 21, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
