(1598, '2012-01-23 07:05:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201230005546208.jpg', 'http://www.saksfifthavenue.com/main/WorldOfDesigner.jsp?FOLDER<>folder_id=2534374306388344&PRODUCT<>prd_id=845524446454076&bmUID=jj3iPT2&site_refer=AFF001&siteID=Jv.v1_Wldzg-5MPNrgmikDpRGNEbUbNBYg&LScreativeid=1&LSlinkid=10&LSoid=243401&LSsid=Jv*v1/Wldzg', 'SUPER HOT! TWO Free 8-pc Gift ($151 value)Lancome Gift with Purchase @ Saks', '<strong >SUPER HOT!</strong> Update : If you input&nbsp; LANCOME4A ,&nbsp; LANCOME4B&nbsp; separately , &nbsp;you will get <strong >&nbsp;</strong><strong >TWO 8-pc gifts</strong><strong >!</strong> &nbsp; That''s super hot! At Saks, through January 29 or while supplies last with any $65 Lancome purchase you can choose a free eight piece gift valued at $151 : <ul><li>Visionnaire Serum</li><li>Absolue Premium Bx Creme SPF 15</li><li>La Base Pro Perfecting Makeup Primer</li><li>Hypnose Doll Lashes Mascara</li><li>Bi-Facil</li><li>Exclusive cosmetic bag&nbsp;designed by Sophie Theallet</li><li>For the <strong>warm</strong> gift enter code <strong >LANCOME4A</strong>, includes&nbsp;Color Design Eye Shadow Quad in Honeymoon, Kitten Heel, Platform, and Madison Avenue plus L’Absolu Rouge Lipcolor in Voile De Rose</li><li>For the <strong>cool</strong> gift enter code <strong >LANCOME4B</strong>, includes Color Design Eye Shadow Quad in Pink Pearls, Lavendar Girl, Clock Strikes 12, and Sultry Mauve plus L’Absolu Rouge Lipcolor in Fleur De Lis</li></ul>', 19, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
