(1600, '2012-01-23 07:11:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201230011064809.jpg', 'http://usa.loccitane.com/FO/Error.aspx?code=404&referer=/FO/Lucky-Bag,p937133.htm?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-User-_-Default-_-None', 'LOccitane Lucky Bag (a $98 value) for $45 + free shipping', '<p> L’Occitane is having the Lucky Bag for $45 (it is a $98 value) + free shipping . It includes Shea Vanilla Shower Cream 16.9 oz, Shea Soap Orange Honey 3.5 oz, Rose 4 Reines Bath &amp; Body Lotion 2.5 oz, and these mystery products: Two travel sized shower products, a travel sized moisturizer, a full size lip gloss, and a bath treat.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(1601, '2012-01-23 07:13:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201230013153913.jpg', 'http://www.shop.puma.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-US-Site/en_US/Default-Start?source=GAN_DealsHuaren', 'Puma Store: up to 60% off Semi-Annual Sale', '<p> Puma Store is offering <strong>up to 60% off</strong> select items as Semi-Annual Sale . Shipping starts at $7 but orders of $50 or more qualify for free shipping. Deal ends January 31. Note that it is better than we saw last week when it was up to 40% off.</p>', 22, 'Huaren Fashion'),
