(1613, '2012-01-23 09:11:01', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201230211015048.jpg', 'http://www.sephora.com/promo/beautybonuses/index.jhtml?pageCode=ws', 'Sephora 17 free samples or free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 order', '<p> Sephora is offering a Skincare Sample Bag with 14 samples for free with orders of $25 or more via coupon code “<strong>TRY14</strong>“. Plus another three samples given with each order. Shipping starts at $5.95 or get free shipping with orders of $50 or more. The bag includes eye cream, moisturizer, serum, cleansing oil, day cream, and more. Note that you can also receive a free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 purchase via code <strong>LIPLOVE</strong> at checkout.</p>', 32, 'Huaren Beauty'),
