(1690, '2012-01-23 21:02:46', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201231402465303.png', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,542820,1942285', 'Kohl''s Gold Star Clearance: 60% to 80% off + extra 20% off', 'Kohl''s cuts <strong>60% to 80% off</strong> items in its Gold Star Clearance . Plus, coupon code "GIFT20" takes an <strong>extra 20% off</strong>. That''s tied with our mention from last week and it''s among the largest percent-off discounts we''ve seen from Kohl''s in recent months. Shipping starts at <b>$5.95</b>, but orders over $75 qualify for free shipping. Sales tax is added where applicable. Coupon expires January 24.<p>A best bet is the Method Space-Dyed Mock-Layer T-Shirt in five colors (Ebony pictured) for <b>$7.68</b> after the above coupon. With <b>$5.95</b> for shipping, that''s $24 off and the lowest total price we could find. It''s available in sizes S and L, although not every size/color combination is available.</p>', 21, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1691, '2012-01-23 21:06:02', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201231406027963.png', 'http://www.dentalplans.com/search/comparedentaldiscountplans.asp', '10% Off + 3 Month Free @ DentalPlans.com', '<ul><li> DentalPlans.com offers 3 Months Free when you join 1 year of Discount Dental Plan membership </li><li> Get&nbsp; Additional 10% off with DealForGirl Exclusive coupon code DealForGirl10 (note: Discount does not apply to California Residents due to state law difference) </li><li> It provide 10% - 60% discount on Teeth Cleaning, Checkups, Fillings, Teeth Removal, Braces &amp; more </li><li> Compare between 30+ different Discount Dental Plans which include 100,000+ Dentists </li><li> Enter Your Zip Code and Compare Dental Discount Plans NOW! </li></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(1692, '2012-01-23 21:06:04', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201231406042863.png', 'http://www.smashbox.com/shared/linkshare.tmpl?siteID=Jv.v1_Wldzg-LoViCoiUdWd7tS84sX79IA&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smashbox.com%2Foffers%2Findex.tmpl%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-Jv*v1/Wldzg-_-null-_-nullJv.v1_Wldzg-LoViCoiUdWd7tS84sX79IA', '$10 off $50 at Smashbox.com', '<ul><li> Last day! Smashbox is offering $10 off with $50 purchase &nbsp;via coupon code " <b >SWEETDEAL</b> ". </li><li> Offer ends 2012-01-22 23:59. </li><li> Free sample with any purchase. </li><li> Interested in learning how to do the Smoky Eye makeup? See this useful Smashbox video here. </li></ul>', 18, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(1693, '2012-01-23 21:06:05', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201231406057595.jpg', 'http://www.coastal.com/', 'FREE Coastal Contacts coupon: Pair of glasses', '<ul><li> Coastal Contacts offers a pair of glasses with lenses for free via coupon code " FIRSTPAIRFREE ". </li><li>Shipping starts around <strong>$10</strong> and includes a mandatory shipping insurance fee that varies based on the value of the frames. </li><li>Note: If you have already received a free pair of glasses via a similar promotion from Coastal Contacts, you are not eligible.</li></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
