(1697, '2012-01-23 22:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120123/201201231502413806.jpg', 'http://www.endofretail.com/?utm_campaign=dealnews&utm_medium=cpc&utm_source=dealnews', 'Fuschia Shamballa Bracelet for $9 + $4 s&h', 'Today only, End of Retail offers the Fuschia Shamballa Bracelet for <strong>$8.95</strong> plus <strong>$3.99</strong> for shipping. That''s the lowest total price we could find for a comparable bracelet by $9. It features resin beads encrusted with fuschia crystals, pull-string closure, and more.', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing');
