(1770, '2012-01-24 07:11:04', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240011049598.jpg', 'http://www.saksfifthavenue.com/main/ProductArray.jsp?FOLDER%3C%3Efolder_id=2534374306570416&bmUID=jkand6v&N=306570416&SECSLOT=LN-Special+Offers&site_refer=AFF001&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-EU4fhFyKrF8vjW8VHIaHGw&LScreativeid=1&LSlinkid=10&LSoid=203719&LSsid=piaqBdsdpmQ', 'Saks La Mer, YSL Beauty, Guerlain, La Prairie, Jo Malone, and more Gift with Purchase', '<p> Saks is having several nice new gifts with purchase today, from La Mer, YSL Beauty, Guerlain, La Prairie, Jo Malone, and more . Plus spend $100 on beauty and you will receive a free silver faux python clutch with code <strong>FETESET</strong> at checkout, that is available through January 29 or while supplies last.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(1771, '2012-01-24 07:11:05', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240011054510.jpg', 'http://www.clinique.com/linkshare.tmpl?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-exp-_-null-_-null&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-52LpNyJkV1i339pxOKwO3g&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clinique.com%2Fcheckout%2Fsamples.tmpl%3FLOCALE%3Den%5FUS%26show%5Fpromo%3D1', 'Clinique free shipping and three free bonus sample products w/ any order', '<p> Ending today (1/12)! Clinique is offering free shipping on any via coupon code &#8220;<strong>SKIN</strong>&#8220;. Plus, receive three free bonus sample products with any purchase. Choose from six extra sample products, such as fragrance, eye cream and makeup remover.</p>', 26, 'Huaren Beauty'),
