(1774, '2012-01-24 08:09:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240109036684.jpg', 'http://canvas.landsend.com/ix/index.html?search=387356+or+387358+or+391461+or+391462+or+400164+or+400165+or+405373+or+405374+or+385754+or+386862+or+405454+or+400184+or+405480+or+405481+&store=lecanvas&action=newSearch&pageSize=72&cm_mmc=Affiliate-_-DEEPLINK-_-TXT-_-xxxx&af_id=linkshare', 'Lands End Canvas Women''s &amp; Men''s Shirts Sale + Free Shipping: Women''s Cotton Modal V-Neck Tee for $7, More', '<li> [Exp. 01/23]<li>Shipping is free via Lands'' End Coupon Code <b>FREEZE</b> and PIN <b>1710</b> [Exp. 01/27]</li> <li><b>Women''s</b><br />* Women''s Vintage Striped Tee for $7<br />* Women''s Cotton Modal V-Neck Tee for $7<br />* Women''s Cotton Modal Crewneck Tee for $7<br />* Women''s Super Lightweight Striped Funnelneck for $7<br />* More ... <br /><li><b>Men''s</b><br />* The Heritage V-neck Tee for $7<br />* The Heritage Crewneck Tee for $7<br />* The Heritage Striped Crewneck Tee for $7<br />* The Heritage Long Sleeve Crewneck Tee for $7<br />* More ...', 23, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
