(1793, '2012-01-24 12:11:17', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240511178904.jpg', 'http://www.kgbdeals.com/national/deals/69371/50-discount-on-beauty-merchandise-at-bloomcom?PID=1969400&utm_source=cj', 'Bloom.com $50 GC for $25', '<p> Today (1/12) only! KGB Deals is offering $50 Bloom.com Gift Certificate for only<strong> $25</strong>. It is 50% off and one of the best deal for bloom.com .</p>', 22, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(1794, '2012-01-24 13:02:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240602487130.png', 'http://www.gillyhicks.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/CategoryDisplay?catalogId=11555&storeId=13607&langId=-1&topCategoryId=21408&categoryId=80625&parentCategoryId=75949', 'Gilly Hicks Down Undies Sale: 1 pair of panties for $3 + free shipping', 'Gilly Hicks offers one pair of select panties for <strong>$2.90</strong> with <b>free shipping</b> via the directions below. That''s at least $8 off and the lowest total prices we''ve seen on panties from Gilly Hicks. Sales tax is added where applicable. Choose from thongs, bloomers, shorts, and more. They come in sizes XS to L, although not all size/style combinations are available. To get this deal: <ol><li>Click here and subscribe to Gilly Hicks'' newsletter</li><li>wait for your confirmation email, which will contain your free shipping code</li><li>click here and add a pair of panties to your shopping cart for <b>$2.90</b></li><li>use the free shipping code from your confirmation email to score <b>free shipping</b></li></ol>', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1795, '2012-01-24 13:06:01', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240606015125.jpg', 'http://www.skinstore.com/tools-skin-care-products.aspx?AID=10273952&PID=2165238&SID=homepage&avs=Brand|Clarisonic&avs=Tools|Y&avn=category|category_root|5|SkinCare&as=Special(Descending)', 'Skinstore Coupon: 15% OFF Site-wide, including Clarisonic Mia', '<ul><li> SkinStore.com&nbsp;offers&nbsp; 15% off Storewide with code&nbsp; 15JAN </li><li>DealForGirl recommends&nbsp;</li><ul><li> Clarisonic Mia &nbsp;for $119 - 15% Off via code&nbsp; 15JAN &nbsp;&nbsp; = $101.15 </li></ul></ul><ul><li> Benefits Beyond Clean Skin </li><ul><li>Sonic skin cleansing improves skin tone, reduces the appearance of pore size and helps skin care products work their best.</li></ul><ul><li>The Clarisonic Skin Cleansing System uses a patented sonic frequency of more than 300 movements per second to clean, soften and smooth skin. In just 60 seconds, the micro-massage action removes 6X more makeup and 2X more dirt and oil than cleansing with your hands alone. Removing more dirt and oil from your pores also helps products work more effectively.</li></ul></ul>', 24, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(1796, '2012-01-24 13:06:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240606034627.jpg', 'https://secure.frs.com/frscart/(X(1)S(0iripyd1kfgwvxcsy2zlyww5))/details_bottles.aspx?AspxAutoDetectCookieSupport=1', '$12 FRS Healthy Protein 12-oz. Drink 12-Pack', 'FRS Healthy Performance offers its FRS Healthy Protein 12-oz. Whey Protein Drink 12-Pack in Blackberry Acai, Peach Mango, or Cherry Limeade for <strong>$12</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>.', 22, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(1797, '2012-01-24 13:13:25', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240613259144.jpg', 'http://shop.reebok.com/US/search?t=NFL', 'Reebok 50% off NFL apparel', '<p> Reebok is taking<strong> 50% off</strong> all men&#8217;s, women&#8217;s and kids&#8217; NFL apparel via coupon code &#8220;<strong>PLAYOFFS</strong>&#8220;. Shipping adds $5 or get free shipping on orders over $79.</p>', 31, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(1798, '2012-01-24 13:17:28', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240617285630.png', 'http://www.roamans.com/Default.aspx?affiliate_id=008&affiliate_location_id=41&WT%2Emc_id=k54384&mid=j102496k54384', 'Roaman''s: 25% off highest-priced item', '25% off highest-priced item Code: RD25EXPRESS Note: Plus, free express shipping upgrade. Exclusions apply. Expires: 01/25/2012', 18, 'dealcoupon Clothing'),
(1799, '2012-01-24 14:02:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240702544644.jpg', 'http://www.lolshirts.com/products/a-salt-with-a-deadly-weapon-t-shirt--2?clickid=0004b7469798a1f80a4286a3604907da', 'LOL Shirts coupon: $4 off all T-shirts + $2 s&h', 'Today only, LOL Shirts takes <strong>$4 off</strong> all T-shirts via coupon code "TAKE4OFF". With <strong>$1.99</strong> for shipping, that''s the best sitewide discount we''ve seen from LOL Shirts since November, when we saw all shirts for $7. They''re available in sizes S to XL at this price; sizes XXL and 3XL are also available, but for 99 cents more.<p>A best bet after discount is the A Salt With A Deadly Weapon T-Shirt in Ash (pictured) for <strong>$5.99</strong> plus <strong>$1.99</strong> for shipping. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $2. It''s available in sizes M to XL; sizes XXL and 3XL are 99 cents more.</p>', 20, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(1800, '2012-01-24 14:02:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201240702541228.jpg', 'http://www.overstock.com/Luggage-Bags/Travel-Select-Oregon-4-piece-Expandable-Luggage-Set/5974404/product.html?cid=143921&fp=F&TRACK=CSENextag&mr:referralID=0028d3c5-4694-11e1-a1f9-001b2166c2c0', 'Travel Select Oregon 4-Piece Expandable Luggage Set for $70 + $3 s&h', 'Overstock.com offers the Travel Select Oregon 4-Piece Expandable Luggage Set in Black/Grey, Blue, or Chocolate, model no. TS4900, for <strong>$69.99</strong> plus <strong>$2.95</strong> for shipping. That''s the lowest total price we could find by $12. This set includes a 29" upright, 25" upright, 21" upright, and 11" boarding bag.', 20, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
