(1901, '2012-01-25 06:02:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201242302446914.jpg', 'http://www.drjays.com/shop/G1-R209490/outerwear-sale-men.html?utm_medium=dealnews&utm_source=cse', 'Dr. Jays coupon: Extra 55% off outerwear, deals from $2 + $5 s&h, more', 'Dr. Jays takes an <strong>extra 55% off</strong> men''s, women''s, and kids'' outerwear via coupon code "OUT55". That''s tied for the largest percent-off discount we''ve seen from Dr. Jays. (We listed an extra 55% off orders of $50 or more last week, since expired.) After discount, deals start at <b>$2.21</b>. Shipping starts at <b>$4.95</b>.<p>A best bet is the Dr. Jays Men''s Bubble Jacket in Red (pictured) for $22.99 before the coupon, <b>$10.35</b> after. With <b>$9.95</b> for shipping, that''s $50 under list and the lowest total price we could find. It''s available in sizes M to XXL.</p><p>Of note, Dr. Jays still takes <strong>30% off</strong> select items with no minimum purchase required via coupon code "30TAKE". Alternatively, take <strong>35% off</strong> orders of $50 or more via coupon code "35TAKE", or <strong>45% off</strong> off orders of $150 or more via coupon code "45TAKE".</p>', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
