(1909, '2012-01-25 06:11:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120124/201201242311062154.jpg', 'http://shop.elizabetharden.com/family/index.jsp?categoryId=2779912', 'Elizabeth Arden Gift with Purchase', '<p> <strong> </strong> Elizabeth Arden is having a after Holiday Cyber Beauty Buys event with up to 35% off + free shipping on $40 or more. Plus, you can combine the following percent coupon or Gift with Purchase promotions.</p> <ul> <li> Free 33-Piece Deluxe Gift (a $350 value) + free shipping  with $65 or more orders via code: <strong>VDAY33</strong> (Ends 1/27)</li> <li> Free 8-Piece Deluxe Gift + free shipping with any order $27.50 or more via code: <strong>LOVE</strong> (Ends 2/21)</li> <li>With any $40 purchase receive free shipping and choose a free skincare gift. Enter one of these codes at checkout: <strong>CERAMIDE5</strong>, <strong>PREVAGE3</strong>, <strong>EIGHTHOUR4</strong>, or <strong>INTERVENE4</strong>.</li> <li>20% off entire order via coupon code &#8220;<strong>NEWYEARS20</strong>&#8220;</li> <li> 15-Piece Luxe Collection for $29.5 with any Elizabeth Arden Purchase </li> </ul> <p>Note that you can add 33-Piece Holiday Color Collection ($350 value) Just $45 with ANY $27.50 purchase.<strong> </strong>Note that you may combine this offer with above codes to maximize your purchase.<strong><br /> </strong></p>', 17, 'Huaren Beauty'),
