(1977, '2012-01-25 15:06:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201250806359680.jpg', 'http://www.sharkstores.com/For-Her?data1=VHhRd3pBb0JDeHdBQUI4QXFZNEFBQUdL&a_aid=8', '$9 3-Piece Bumpits Hair Volumizing Inserts 2-Pack', 'Today only (Jan 16), SharkStores offers 3-Piece Bumpits Hair Volumizing Inserts 2-Pack in Dark Brown / Black (pictured), Blonde, or Light Brown for <strong>$9</strong> plus $1.99 for shipping.', 15, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
