(1983, '2012-01-25 16:02:47', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201250902471527.png', 'http://www.ctshirts.com/default.aspx?q=share||||||||||||||&cm_mmc=Affiliates-_-LSUS-_-text_homepage-_-Nov_10', 'Charles Tyrwhitt: Up to 75% off men''s shirts & suits, deals from $35 + $10 s&h', 'Charles Tyrwhitt takes <strong>up to 75% off</strong> select men''s dress shirts and suits . That''s tied with last week''s mention and the among the best discounts we''ve seen on these items from Charles Tyrwhitt in recent months. (We saw a shirt and tie for $50 shipped in November.) Shipping starts at <strong>$9.95</strong> and sales tax is added where applicable. Deals start at <strong>$35</strong> for men''s dress shirts and <strong>$355</strong> for suits.', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
