(1985, '2012-01-25 16:02:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201250902483191.jpg', 'http://www.vistaprint.com/vp/gateway.asp?S=8600448672&AID=10489577&PID=552179&SID=VHlBbml3b0JDeGdBQUQ4UnYtQUFBQUFJ', 'Vistaprint Custom Printed T-Shirt for free + $4 s&h', 'Vistaprint still offers a Custom-Printed T-Shirt for <strong>free</strong> plus <strong>$4.41</strong> for shipping. That''s tied with last week''s mention as one of the least expensive custom T-shirts we''ve seen. Only front printing is included in the price. (Additional customization is available for an extra cost.) It''s available in sizes from S to XL; XXL is available for an additional $1.99.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
