(2055, '2012-01-26 01:09:14', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251809143300.png', 'http://www.lastcall.com/p/Laundry-by-Shelli-Segal-Cap-Sleeve-Draped-Neck-Dress-Dresses/prod8240021/?srccode=cii_16079562&cpncode=30-23933326-2&=&ecid=LCCIBecomeFeed&ncx=n&uEm=%25%25CSE%25%25', '40% OFF Last Call by Neiman Marcus Sale: 40% off one item', '<ul><li>Today only (Jan 24), Last Call by Neiman Marcus takes <strong>40% off</strong> one regular-priced item. (Discount appears in cart). </li><li>Plus, orders over $75 receive free shipping via coupon code " LC75JAN ". (Otherwise, shipping starts at <b>$5</b>.) Some highlights:</li><ul><li> Rock &amp; Republic Men''s Teresa Straight-Leg Jeans for <strong>$59.40</strong></li><li> Laundry by Shelli Segal Women''s Cap-Sleeve Draped-Neck Dress (pictured) for <strong>$72</strong></li><li> John Varvatos Men''s Schooner Suede Boat Shoes for <strong>$77.40</strong></li><li> BCBGMAXAZRIA Women''s Tiered Illusion-Neck Dress for <strong>$101.40</strong></li><li>see more eligible items at Last Call by Neiman Marcus </li></ul></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
