(2057, '2012-01-26 01:13:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251813441406.jpg', 'http://www.classicshapewear.com/all-over-lace-babydoll-with-eyelash-lace-trims-amy8-p-3295.html?osCsid=434cb02420fbd18395e841196a89815a', 'Classic Shapewear Womens All Over Lace Babydoll Lingerie Set for $10', '<p> Classic Shapewear is offering the Classic Shapewear Women&#8217;s All Over Lace Babydoll Lingerie Set in Black, Fuchsia, or Red for $39 &#8211; coupon code &#8220;<strong>VDAY</strong>&#8221; = <strong>$9.99 </strong>with free shipping. It&#8217;s available in sizes S to XL. They also have the Classic Shapewear Women&#8217;s Lace Teddy with Tie Front in Black/Fuchsia for <strong>$9.99</strong> as well after the coupon above with free shipping. It&#8217;s available in sizes S to 3XL.</p>', 25, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2058, '2012-01-26 02:02:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251902368623.png', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,543623,1945455', 'Last Call by Neiman Marcus Her Him & Home Sale: Extra 30% to 50% off', 'Last Call by Neiman Marcus takes an <strong>extra 30% to 50% off</strong> during its Her Him & Home Sale . (Discount appears in cart). Plus, orders over $75 receive free shipping via coupon code "LC75JAN". (Otherwise, shipping starts at <b>$5</b>.) That''s among the best sales we''ve seen from Last Call in recent weeks. (We saw 40% off one regular-price item yesterday, since expired.) Sales tax is added where applicable. Deal ends January 30.<p>A best bet is the BCBGMAXAZRIA Women''s Metal Mesh Clutch (pictured) for <b>$50</b> in-cart. With <b>$5</b> for shipping, that''s $78 off and the lowest total price we could find.</p>', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2059, '2012-01-26 02:06:45', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251906455944.jpg', 'http://www.burtsbees.com/?cm_mmc=CJ-_-1899918-_-2165238-_-Burt%27s+Bees+Home+Page', '$15 Burt''s Bees Grab Bag', '<ul><li>Burt''s Bees offers its Burt''s Bees Grab Bag for <strong>$15</strong>.</li><li>Shipping costs <strong >$5</strong>, or spend $49 to get shipping for free.&nbsp;</li><li>Each includes five full-sized products, an assortment of mini-size products, and special gifts. All sales are final. </li></ul>', 20, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2060, '2012-01-26 02:08:55', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251908559635.jpg', 'http://www5.snapfish.com/snapfish/storepage/storePageId=Store_Offers_Page/campaignName=commissionjunction_specialoffers?AID=10731220&PID=552179&SID=VHg5UW93b0JDalVBQUE2dlM4Y0FBQUtB&source=cjcmpg&URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww5.snapfish.com%2Fsnapfish%2Fstorepage%2FstorePageId%3DStore_Offers_Page%2FcampaignName%3Dcommissionjunction_specialoffers%3FAID%3D10731220%26PID%3D552179%26SID%3DVHg5UW93b0JDalVBQUE2dlM4Y0FBQUtB%26source%3Dcjcmpg', 'Snapfish coupons: 70% off 11-oz. Photo Mugs, 40% off Valentine''s Shop', '<ul><li>Snapfish cuts <strong>70% off</strong> 11-oz. Photo Mugs via coupon code " LOVE70 ". Or, take <strong>40% off</strong> Valentine Cards, Photo Books, Jewelry, and more with " LOVE40 ".</li><li>Shipping starts at $1.99.&nbsp;</li><li>Deal expires January 25.</li></ul>', 18, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(2061, '2012-01-26 02:11:08', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120125/201201251911083488.jpg', 'http://www.groupon.com/deals/diamond-toothbrush-pittsburgh-1?utm_medium=afl&utm_campaign=1969400&utm_source=rvs', 'Diamond Elite Ultrasonic Toothbrush for $69', '<p> Groupon is offering the Diamond Elite Ultrasonic Toothbrush for <strong>$69</strong> with free shipping. It features a UV sanitizing charger base, three replacement brush heads, and more. Coupon is valid through October 6 at 1 am ET. Note that although this is listed in Groupon Corpus Christi, it can be purchased and used by anyone.</p>', 35, 'Huaren Beauty'),
