(2229, '2012-01-27 01:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120126/201201261802414744.png', 'http://oakleyvault.com/product/arctic-challenge-beanie/91485-21P?cm_mmc=CJ-_-AFFILIATE-_-552179-_-10676668', 'Oakley Accessories at Oakley Vault: Up to 70% off, deals from $7 + $7 s&h', 'Oakley Vault cuts <b>up to 70% off</b> a selection of men''s and women''s accessories , with deals starting at <strong>$7.49</strong>. That''s the best deal we''ve seen on these items from Oakley Vault since November, when we saw up to 80% off. Sales tax is added where applicable. Shipping starts at <b>$6.58</b>, or get free shipping on orders over $100.<p>A best bet is the Oakley Men''s Artic Challenge Beanie in Neutral Grey (pictured), Enamel Mint, or Red Line for <strong>$7.49</strong> plus <strong>$6.58</strong> for shipping. That''s the lowest toal price we could find by $18. Sales tax is added where applicable. This 10"-deep beanie features a 50% polyester/50% acrylic construction.</p>', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
