(2311, '2012-01-27 10:13:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270313353917.jpg', 'http://www.swarovski.com/Web_US/en/91109/category?AID=10407424&CJPID=1969400&SID=dealshr_15344_1', 'Swarovski online sale 50% off select items', '<p> <em> </em> Swarovski has its online sale going on. All sale items are<strong> 50% off</strong> select sale items as listed below. Free shipping for order over $95. Plus a free greeting card and gift bag with any purchase. <em>update :</em> <em>now you can get <strong>an extra 10% off</strong> regular-price items of $155 or more </em>via coupon code &#8220;<strong>VALENTINE2012</strong>&#8220;.</p> <ul> <li> On sale Specials </li> <li> On sale Classics </li> <li> On sale Fashionables </li> <li> On sale Figurines </li> <li> On sale accessories </li> <li> On sale Charms </li> <li> On sale Men&#8217;s </li> <li> On sale Rings </li> <li> On sale Glasses </li> <li> On Sale Watches </li> </ul>', 13, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2312, '2012-01-27 10:17:14', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270317144106.png', 'http://a248.e.akamai.net/f/248/45320/14d/ig.rsys2.net/responsysimages/content/kohls/012612_printpass_yes.htm', 'Kohls: 20% off no min coupon', '20% off no min coupon Note: Printable, for use in-stores. Exclusions apply. Expires: 01/28/2012', 18, 'dealcoupon Clothing'),
(2313, '2012-01-27 11:02:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270402439328.png', 'http://shnoop.com/', 'Wonderbra Lace Hi-Cut Stretch Panty Brief 4-Pack for $14 + free shipping', 'Today only, until 9 pm ET, Shnoop offers the Wonderbra Lace Hi-Cut Stretch Panty Brief 4-Pack , model no. W4512, for $14.99. Coupon code "DealForGirl1" cuts it to <strong>$13.99</strong>. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that''s $24 under the lowest total price we could find for this quantity of Wonderbra panties elsewhere. They''re available in sizes M to 3XL and will ship in random colors.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2314, '2012-01-27 11:02:44', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270402447007.png', 'http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?b=294658&u=314743&m=31917&afftrack=skim1043X499650Xf47d0796b2e92e15becbd5da039c2bfd&urllink=www.o2gearshop.com%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct_info.php%3FcPath%3D2%26language%3Den%26currency%3DUSD%26products_id%3D38353%26zmam%3D55982562%26zmas%3D1%26zmac%3D8%26zmap%3D38353', 'The North Face Women''s Khumbu Fleece Jacket for $53 + free shipping', 'O2 Gear Shop Outlet still offers The North Face Women''s Khumbu Fleece Jacket in six colors (Olivetto Green pictured) for <strong>$52.95</strong> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s tied with last week''s mention and the lowest total price we could find for this jacket in any color by $10. It''s available in sizes XS to XL, although not in all size/color combinations.', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2315, '2012-01-27 11:05:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270405566257.png', 'http://www.origins.com/linkshare.tmpl?siteID=Jv.v1_Wldzg-jvE5xylHwHiPAc2qZglE_A&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.origins.com%2Findex.tmpl%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-Jv*v1/Wldzg-_-null-_-null', 'Origins Coupon: Free Shipping plus choose a free deluxe sample', '<ul><li><strong></strong> Origins offers: with any purchase receive free shipping plus choose a free deluxe sample . </li><ul><li>Enter code <strong>BONUS1</strong> for A Perfect World Antioxidant Cleanser with White Tea (1 oz);. </li><li>Enter code <strong>BONUS2</strong> for Zero Oil Deep Pore Cleanser with Saw Palmetto &amp; Mint (0.5&nbsp;oz); </li><li>Enter code <strong>BONUS3</strong> for VitaZing SPF 15 (0.5&nbsp;oz); </li><li>Enter code <strong>BONUS4</strong> for A&nbsp;Perfect World SPF 25 Age-defense Moisturizer with White Tea (0.5 oz). </li></ul><li>Expires Jan 29 or while supplies last.</li></ul>', 20, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2316, '2012-01-27 11:05:57', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270405575802.jpg', 'http://www.esteelauder.com/index.tmpl', 'Free Sample Estee Lauder Coupon: Free shipping and Free Deluxe Samples with $50 purchase', '<ul><li> Estee Lauder offers: with any $50 purchase receive free shipping and free deluxe samples: &nbsp; </li><ul><li>Resilience Lift Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Cream SPF 15</li><li>Resilience Lift Eye Cream. </li></ul><li>Enter code <strong>LIFTDUO </strong>at checkout. </li><li>Expires January 25 or while supplies last.</li></ul>', 17, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2317, '2012-01-27 11:11:14', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270411143374.jpg', 'http://www.lancome-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-lancome_us-Site/default/Home-Show?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-GenericBannerFSandSamples-_-468x60&clickID=dealshr_11574_64&pubID=piaqBdsdpmQ', 'Lancome Gift with Purchase promotions', '<p> Lancome is having Gift with Purchase are listed below. Note that registered members can choose an additional deluxe sample at checkout.</p> <ul> <li> free shipping + 7-piece Lancome Spring Gift with any $75 or more purchase.</li> <li> 4 piece sample set (a $148 Value) plus Free Shipping with order of $45 or more via coupon code: <strong>NEWYEARLAN</strong></li> </ul>', 19, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2318, '2012-01-27 11:11:14', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270411142457.jpg', 'http://www.sephora.com/index.jhtml?om_mmc=aff-linkshare-homepage-piaqBdsdpmQ&_requestid=1877', 'Sephora 17 free samples or free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &#038; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 order', '<p> Sephora is offering a Skincare Sample Bag with 14 samples for free with orders of $25 or more via coupon code &#8220;<strong>TRY14</strong>&#8220;. Plus another three samples given with each order. Shipping starts at $5.95 or get free shipping with orders of $50 or more. The bag includes eye cream, moisturizer, serum, cleansing oil, day cream, and more. Note that you can also receive a free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 purchase via code <strong>LIPLOVE</strong> at checkout.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2319, '2012-01-27 11:13:21', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270413212830.jpg', 'http://www.ae.com/web/index.jsp', 'American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle extra 40% off clearance + extra 15% off coupon', '<p> American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle are taking an <strong>extra 40% off</strong> clearance items. (Discount is applied in-cart.) Even better, apply  coupon code &#8220;<strong>60255011</strong>&#8221; to get an <strong>additional 15% off</strong>. Shipping starts at $7 or get free shipping with orders of $100 or more.</p>', 15, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2320, '2012-01-27 12:02:40', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270502409971.jpg', 'http://www.ice.com/bracelets/gemstone-bracelet-prd_bcy_122539.jsp?srccode=cii_5784816&cpncode=27-90461617-2', 'ICE.com: $20 off regularly-priced jewelry of $20 or more + free shipping', 'ICE.com takes <strong>$20 off</strong> most regularly-priced orders of $20 or more via coupon code "S20AU". Plus, all items qualify for <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s tied with our mention from last week as one of the best dollar-off coupons we''ve seen from ICE.com in recent weeks. (We saw a coupon for $25 off items of $25 or more in December.) Note that sale items, clearance, engagement rings, and bridal rings are excluded from the discount.<p>A best bet is the Blue Turquoise and Prehnite Bracelet (pictured), model no. BCY 122539, for $45 before the coupon above, <strong>$25</strong> after. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that''s the lowest total price we could find for such a bracelet.</p>', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2321, '2012-01-27 12:06:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270506064516.png', 'http://www.kiehls.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-kiehls_us-Site/default/Home-Show?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-Generic-_-Any', 'Free samples! Kiehl''s：Two Free Deluxe Samples with purchase of NEW Clearly Corrective', '<ul><li> Kiehls offers two free samples (Deluxe Midnight Recovery Concentrate &amp; Rosa Arctica) with&nbsp;purchase of NEW Clearly Corrective &nbsp; via coupon code " <b >RADIANT</b> ".&nbsp; </li><li> Offer ends 2012-03-16. </li></ul>', 16, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2322, '2012-01-27 12:06:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270506064788.jpg', 'http://www.dermstore.com/profile_blowoutboutique_501933.htm?utm_source=cj&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_term=blowout_text&utm_campaign=cj_20120123&AID=10700193&PID=2165238&source=cj', '$12 Dermstore Blowout Sale：beauty products', '<ul><li>Dermstore offers select beauty products for <strong>$12</strong> during its Blowout Sale . </li><li>Plus, all orders receive <strong>free shipping</strong> with no minimum purchase required.</li><li>Deal expires February 1.</li><li>DealForGirl recommends: the iQ Derma Clear Remedy Acne Treatment Kit (pictured) for <strong>$12</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>.&nbsp;</li></ul>', 18, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2323, '2012-01-27 12:09:16', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270509168626.jpg', 'http://www.jcpenney.com/jcp/X6.aspx?Grptyp=PRD&ItemId=1c56c0f&sisearchengine=186&siproduct=AFFILIATE&cm_mmc=LinkShare-_-AFF-_-Mktg-_-Ad', 'Arizona Colorblock Toddler Girls Coat', '<li> Use 15% off JCPenney Coupon Code <b>12JANAPP</b></li> <li> Free shipping to your store. </li> She won''t mind putting on this stylish girls coat to play outside. It will keep her warm and fashionable  plus, it includes coordinating mittens to keep her little paws warm.<br />Girls Coat:<br />colorblock design with piping<br />zip/snap front<br />detachable hood<br />back heart embroidery<br />long sleeves with self-adhesive tabs on elastic cuffs<br />2 front pockets<br />includes mittens<br />polyester, with polyester lining<br />washable<br />imported', 15, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(2324, '2012-01-27 13:02:41', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270602416725.jpg', 'http://www.dealgenius.com/showproduct.aspx?ProductID=3130&SEName=winter-flap-hat-random-color-one-size-fits-most', 'Winter Accessories: Up to 87% off, hats and more for $2 + free shipping', 'Deal Genius continues to cut <strong>up to 87% off</strong> a selection of winter apparel and accessories, as listed below. Plus, coupon code "LOYAL5" cuts an <strong>additional 5% off</strong>. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, each is tied with our mention from three weeks ago and at the lowest total price we could find. The deals, with prices after the coupon above:<ul><li> Winter Flap Hat (pictured) for <strong>$1.89</strong></li><li> Winter Fleece Headband for <strong>$1.89</strong></li><li> Kenny Hwang Beanie Skull Caps Tattoo Wear 2-Pack for <strong>$1.89</strong></li><li> Lightweight 5-LED Cap Light for <strong>$1.89</strong></li></ul>', 21, 'Dealnews Clothing');
