(2325, '2012-01-27 13:16:36', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270616368919.png', 'http://www.celebrateexpress.com/?REF=AFC-cetext&AID=10641229&PID=552179&SID=VHlLamtnb0JDeHdBQUI1MHAyd0FBQUVO', 'Celebrate Express: 15% off any order.', '15% off any order. Code: YOUSAVE15 Note: Exclusions apply. Expires: 01/27/2012', 14, 'dealcoupon Clothing'),
(2326, '2012-01-27 14:02:49', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270702495273.png', 'http://www.eddiebauer.com/catalog/product.jsp?ensembleId=41128&oessoa=6046151&cm_mmc=CSE-_-Shopping_com-_-Men%7cSweaters-_-1039066', 'Men''s Sweaters at Eddie Bauer: 40% off + extra 20% off, deals from $10 + $8 s&h', 'Eddie Bauer takes <strong>40% off</strong> select men''s sweaters, as listed below. (The discount is applied in cart.) Plus, coupon code "BADCQ3411" takes an <strong>extra 20% off</strong>. Combined, it''s one of the best offers we''ve seen for these items from Eddie Bauer in recent weeks. (We listed up to 66% off sweaters plus an extra 15% off in December.) Shipping starts at <strong>$7.99</strong> and sales tax is added where applicable. Some best bets:<ul><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s Marl Fatigue Sweater (pictured) for <strong>$9.59</strong></li><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s Cotton/Cashmere Button Sweater for <strong>$11.99</strong></li><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s 1920 Collection Nailhead Sweater for <strong>$47.99</strong></li><li>browse all men''s sweaters on sale at Eddie Bauer </li></ul>', 15, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2327, '2012-01-27 14:02:50', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270702507366.jpg', 'http://www.everydaysource.com/product/Silver-Square-Diagonal-Ribbed-Cufflinks/MOTHCUFLINK3', 'Silver Square Diagonal Ribbed Cufflinks for $4 + free shipping', 'For its newsletter subscribers only, EverydaySource offers these Silver Square Diagonal Ribbed Cufflinks for $5.49. Coupon code "S0126WSEG" drops them to <strong>$4.19</strong>. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that''s $5 under the lowest total price we could find for similar cufflinks elsewhere. These cufflinks are rhodium plated with a diagonal pattern.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2328, '2012-01-27 14:07:35', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270707352343.jpg', 'http://www.fractionprice.com/detail.asp?iq=1&bo_products_id=&bo_products_variance_id=112805&promotion_code=DDS2312612112805', '$52.11 ($75,31% off) adidas Unisex Cambridge Polyurethane Watch', 'today only (jan 26), fractionprice offers adidas unisex cambridge polyurethane watch in baby blue for <strong>$52.11 </strong>with <strong>free shipping</strong>.', 16, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(2329, '2012-01-27 14:09:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201270709035115.jpg', 'http://www.skinstore.com/tools-skin-care-products.aspx?AID=10273952&PID=2165238&SID=homepage&avs=Brand|Clarisonic&avs=Tools|Y&avn=category|category_root|5|SkinCare&as=Special(Descending)', 'Skinstore Coupon: 20% OFF Site-wide, including Clarisonic Mia', '<ul><li> SkinStore.com&nbsp;offers&nbsp; 20% off Storewide with code&nbsp; FAB20 </li><li>DealForGirl recommends&nbsp;</li><ul><li> Clarisonic Mia &nbsp;for $119 - 20% Off via code&nbsp; FAB20 &nbsp;&nbsp; = $95.2 </li><li> Clarisonic Plus for $225 - 20% Off = $180 </li><li> Clarisonic Mia 2 (2 speeds) for $149 - 20% Off = $119.2 </li><li> Clarisonic Replacement Brush Head for $25 - 20% Off = $20 </li></ul></ul><ul><li> Benefits Beyond Clean Skin </li><ul><li>Sonic skin cleansing improves skin tone, reduces the appearance of pore size and helps skin care products work their best.</li></ul><ul><li>The Clarisonic Skin Cleansing System uses a patented sonic frequency of more than 300 movements per second to clean, soften and smooth skin. In just 60 seconds, the micro-massage action removes 6X more makeup and 2X more dirt and oil than cleansing with your hands alone. Removing more dirt and oil from your pores also helps products work more effectively.</li></ul></ul>', 23, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
