(2435, '2012-01-28 06:02:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120127/201201272302432911.jpg', 'http://www.shoemall.com/catalog/search.cmd?form_state=searchForm&searchterm=boots&AID=10964455&PID=552179&SID=VHlPUFl3b0JDeHdBQUIzejZJb0FBQUNv&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=551655&utm_source=dealnews.com', 'ShoeMall coupon: 25% off all boots + free shipping', 'ShoeMall takes <strong>25% off</strong> men''s, women''s, and kids'' boots with no minimum purchase required via coupon code "BOOTS25". Plus, all orders qualify for <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the largest percent-off coupon we''ve seen on these items from ShoeMall in recent months. (We saw 25% off sitewide during its Cyber Monday sale, but that deal required a $25 minimum order.) Shop for shoes, watches, handbags, and more. Note that some brands are excluded. Deal ends January 28.', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
