(2486, '2012-01-28 11:55:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455421082.jpg', 'http://www.lancome-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-lancome_us-Site/default/Home-Show?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-GenericBannerFSandSamples-_-468x60&clickID=dealshr_11574_64&pubID=piaqBdsdpmQ', 'Lancome Gift with Purchase promotions', '<p> Lancome is having Gift with Purchase are listed below. Note that registered members can choose an additional deluxe sample at checkout.</p> <ul> <li> free 6-piece sample + free shipping with $50 or more purchase with coupon code: <strong>ONEDAY</strong> (1/27 only)</li> <li> 4 piece sample set (a $148 Value) plus Free Shipping with order of $45 or more via coupon code: <strong>NEWYEARLAN</strong></li> </ul>', 26, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2487, '2012-01-28 11:55:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455425851.jpg', 'http://www.saksfifthavenue.com/main/ProductArray.jsp?FOLDER%3C%3Efolder_id=2534374306570416&bmUID=jkand6v&N=306570416&SECSLOT=LN-Special+Offers&site_refer=AFF001&siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-Ly7Ku.yB8CkQs.tG3LQvHw&LScreativeid=1&LSlinkid=10&LSoid=203719&LSsid=piaqBdsdpmQ', 'Saks La Mer, YSL Beauty, Guerlain, La Prairie, Jo Malone, and more Gift with Purchase', '<p> Saks is having several nice new gifts with purchase today, from La Mer, YSL Beauty, Guerlain, La Prairie, Jo Malone, and more . Plus spend $100 on beauty and you will receive a free silver faux python clutch with code <strong>FETESET</strong> at checkout, that is available through January 29 or while supplies last.</p>', 20, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2488, '2012-01-28 11:55:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455428805.jpg', 'http://www.origins.com/linkshare.tmpl?siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-mL2Z3oZlSQWbPQ1f.mRR5g&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.origins.com%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-piaqBdsdpmQ-_-null-_-null', 'Origins: FREE Perfect World Antioxidant cleanser with White Tea + free shipping with ANY order', '<p> Origins is offering FREE Perfect World Antioxidant cleanser with White Tea + FREE Shipping with any Origins.com purchase. Enter Code <strong>BONUS1 </strong>at checkout. Offer valid thru 2/4. Note that you can choose another free sample at checkout.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2489, '2012-01-28 11:55:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455429804.jpg', 'http://www.sephora.com/index.jhtml?om_mmc=aff-linkshare-homepage-piaqBdsdpmQ&_requestid=4127', 'Sephora 17 free samples or free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &#038; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 order', '<p> Sephora is offering a Skincare Sample Bag with 14 samples for free with orders of $25 or more via coupon code &#8220;<strong>TRY14</strong>&#8220;. Plus another three samples given with each order. Shipping starts at $5.95 or get free shipping with orders of $50 or more. The bag includes eye cream, moisturizer, serum, cleansing oil, day cream, and more. Note that you can also receive a free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 purchase via code <strong>LIPLOVE</strong> at checkout.</p>', 20, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2490, '2012-01-28 11:55:43', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455431285.jpg', 'http://www.bergdorfgoodman.com/store/catalog/templates/silo.jhtml?itemId=cat000005&ecid=BGALRTnL5HPStwNw', 'Bergdorf Goodman Beauty Event', '<p> <strong>Bergdorf Goodman</strong> is having a <strong>Rewarding Beauty Event</strong> . Spend $200 on beauty to receive a cosmetic bag with eleven deluxe samples. There are over 40 GWPs during this event. Free Shipping with any order with code <strong>BTYBAG</strong>.</p>', 17, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2491, '2012-01-28 11:55:56', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280455569325.jpg', 'http://www.ae.com/web/index.jsp', 'American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle extra 40% off clearance + extra 15% off coupon', '<p> American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle are taking an <strong>extra 40% off</strong> clearance items. (Discount is applied in-cart.) Even better, apply  coupon code &#8220;<strong>60255011</strong>&#8221; to get an <strong>additional 15% off</strong>. Shipping starts at $7 or get free shipping with orders of $100 or more.</p>', 20, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2492, '2012-01-28 12:05:48', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280505489903.jpg', 'http://www.esteelauder.com/index.tmpl', 'Free Sample Estee Lauder Coupon: Free shipping and Free Deluxe Samples with $50 purchase', '<ul><li> Estee Lauder offers: with any $50 purchase receive free shipping and free deluxe samples: &nbsp; </li><ul><li>Resilience Lift Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Cream SPF 15</li><li>Resilience Lift Eye Cream. </li></ul><li>Enter code <strong>LIFTDUO </strong>at checkout. </li><li>Expires January 25 or while supplies last.</li></ul>', 22, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2493, '2012-01-28 12:10:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280510548237.jpg', 'http://www.kiehls.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-kiehls_us-Site/default/Home-Show?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-Generic-_-Any', 'Kiehls: free deluxe Midnight Recovery Concentrate &#038; Rosa Arctica with Clearly Corrective purchase', '<p> Kiehl&#8217;s is offering free deluxe Midnight Recovery Concentrate &amp; Rosa Arctica with purchasing Kiehl&#8217;s NEW Clearly Corrective with Code <strong>RADIANT </strong>at checkout. Offer Valid thru 3/15.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2494, '2012-01-28 12:10:54', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280510545730.jpg', 'http://www.dermstore.com/profile_blowout+boutique_501933.htm', 'Dermstore Blowout Sale', '<p> DermStore is having a Blowout Sale with select Beauty Item for $12 each. Free shipping on all orders.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2495, '2012-01-28 12:13:06', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280513067741.jpg', 'http://www.jcpenney.com/jcp/MissingPPError.aspx', 'New Balance Men&#8217;s 310 Running Shoes for $27', '<p> JCPenney is offering the New Balance Men&#8217;s 310 Running Shoes in Black/Red or Black/Yellow for <strong>$27</strong>. Apply coupon code &#8220;<strong>FREESHIP</strong>&#8221; to get free in-store pickup. These shoes are available in sizes 7 to 14.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2496, '2012-01-28 14:07:22', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280707221298.jpg', 'http://www.eddiebauer.com/catalog/product.jsp?ensembleId=41792&oessoa=6046151&cm_mmc=CSE-_-PriceGrabber-_-Men%7cHoodies_and_Sweatshirts-_-1057745&OESSOA=6056709', '25% OFF Eddie Bauer coupon: men''s and women''s apparel', '<ul><li> Eddie Bauer takes <strong>25% off</strong> on regularly-priced men''s and women''s apparel via coupon code "<strong>SPRING12</strong>". </li><li> Shipping starts at $7.99, free shipping on orders over $99. </li><li> Coupon expires February 12. Some highlights: </li><ul><li> Eddie Bauer Women''s 3/4-Sleeve Striped Notch-Neck Favorite T-Shirt for <strong>$22.46</strong> </li><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s Classic Fit Double-Cloth Crew Sweater for <strong>$33.71</strong> </li><li> Eddie Bauer Women''s Duofold Hoodie for <strong>$37.46</strong> </li><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s Classic Fit Vintage Hoodie (pictured in Picante) for <strong>$44.96</strong> </li><li> Eddie Bauer Men''s Travex Convertible Pants for <strong>$52.46</strong> </li><li> browse all Eddie Bauer men''s and women''s regularly-priced apparel for more buying ideas </li></ul></ul>', 18, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(2497, '2012-01-28 14:11:08', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280711085324.jpg', 'http://www.skinstore.com/?AID=4198913&PID=1969400&SID=dealshr_15385_1', 'Skinstore extra 20% off sitewide, Clarisonic Mia 2 for $119', '<p> SkinStore is offering <strong>20% off</strong> Storewide via coupon code: <strong>CUPID20</strong>. Free shipping $49 or more. Note that some exclusions may apply. They have the Clarisonic Mia 2 Sonic Cleansing System &#8211; White for<strong> $119 </strong>after coupon. They also have select premium brands items on sale up to 25% off.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2498, '2012-01-28 14:13:18', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280713185281.jpg', 'http://www.menswearhouse.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/Navigation_-1_10601_10051_10051_/Shoes/@/N-1z141g5Z1z141q6Z1z141yjZ1z141ye/dp-1z141q6__Pprice|0?sort=Pprice|0&searchTerm=&searchType=sort&redirectURL=&top=10051', 'Mens Wearhouse 40% off select mens shoes', '<p> Men&#8217;s Wearhouse is taking<strong> 40% off</strong> Rockport , Dockers , and Belvedere men&#8217;s shoes via coupon code &#8220;<strong>40SHOEM</strong>&#8220;. Shipping starts at $8 but orders of $150 or more qualify for free shipping. (Free ship-to-store is also available.) Deal ends January 30.</p>', 15, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2499, '2012-01-28 15:02:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120128/201201280802424430.jpg', 'http://dealnews.com/lw/click.html?1,2,544517,1950143', 'Puma shoes & apparel: 15% to 72% off, deals from $7 + free shipping', '6pm cuts <strong>15% to 72% off</strong> a selection of Puma men''s , women''s , boys'' and girls'' shoes and apparel items , with prices starting at <strong>$6.99</strong>. With <strong>free shipping</strong>, that puts most items at the lowest total prices we could find. That''s among the best discounts we''ve seen on Puma items from 6pm since October, when we saw up to 83% off.<p>A best bet are these Puma Men''s Running Complete Haraka XCS Shoes in Orange/Black/Lime Punch (pictured) or Lime Punch/Black/Yellow for <strong>$32.50</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>. That''s the lowest total price we could find for any color by $6. It''s available in sizes 4 through 15, but not in all size/color combinations.</p>', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing');
