(2838, '2012-01-30 13:02:42', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300602428572.jpg', 'http://www.sharkstores.com/For-Him?data1=VHlhVXlnb0JDeGtBQURmeVNSRUFBQUVK&a_aid=8', 'Marmot Men''s Aegis Waterproof Jacket for $76 + $6 s&h', 'Today only, SharkStores offers the Marmot Men''s Aegis Waterproof Jacket in four colors (Cardinal pictured) for $79. Coupon code "3DealForGirl3" cuts it to <strong>$76</strong>. With <strong>$5.95</strong> for shipping, that''s the lowest total price we could find in any color by $28, although it was a buck less in August. This jacket features DriClimb-lined cuffs and collar, hood, hand-warmer pockets, and more. It''s available in sizes M to XXL, although not in all color/size combinations.', 20, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2839, '2012-01-30 13:05:52', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300605522191.png', 'http://www.kiehls.com/Special-Offers-from-Kiehl%27s-Since-1851/special-offers-2,default,pg.html?cm_mmc=Linkshare-_-Affiliate-_-Janoffer-_-RADIANT', 'Free samples! Kiehl''s：Two Free Deluxe Samples with purchase of NEW Clearly Corrective', '<ul><li> Kiehls offers two free samples (Deluxe Midnight Recovery Concentrate &amp; Rosa Arctica) with&nbsp;purchase of NEW Clearly Corrective &nbsp; via coupon code " <b >RADIANT</b> ".&nbsp; </li><li> Offer ends 2012-03-16. </li></ul>', 15, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
(2840, '2012-01-30 13:05:52', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300605527681.jpg', 'http://www.dermstore.com/profile_blowoutboutique_501933.htm?utm_source=cj&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_term=blowout_text&utm_campaign=cj_20120123&AID=10700193&PID=2165238&source=cj', '$12 Dermstore Blowout Sale：beauty products', '<ul><li>Dermstore offers select beauty products for <strong>$12</strong> during its Blowout Sale . </li><li>Plus, all orders receive <strong>free shipping</strong> with no minimum purchase required.</li><li>Deal expires February 1.</li><li>DealForGirl recommends: the iQ Derma Clear Remedy Acne Treatment Kit (pictured) for <strong>$12</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>.&nbsp;</li></ul>', 17, 'Dealmoon Beauty'),
