(2847, '2012-01-30 14:09:08', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300709085082.jpg', 'http://www.shopjustice.com/?AID=10593114&PID=2138476&utm_content=1880868&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=%28Expired%29+Justice+234x60+Logo+Only&utm_source=cj_affiliate&utm_term=cj', 'Justice Coupons: 40% off Entire Order Online &amp; In-store', '<li> Shipping starts at $5. </li> Available Justice Coupons and Justice Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>40% off Entire Order Online & In-store</b><br />* Online: Use Justice Coupon Code 779 or 752 [Exp. 02/08] <br />* In-store: In-store Printable Justice Coupon [Exp. 02/08]', 18, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
