(2849, '2012-01-30 15:02:29', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300802292303.jpg', 'http://www.botachtactical.com/rimcev.html', 'Ridge Men''s Evolution Motorcycle Boots for $40 + free shipping', 'Botach Tactical offers <b>DealForGirl</b> readers the Ridge Men''s Evolution Motorcycle Boots with Gray stitching (pictured), model no. MC202GI, or Orange stitching , model no. MC202OI, for $120. Coupon code "DealForGirl" cuts them to <b>$39.60</b>. With <b>free shipping</b>, that''s $80 off and the lowest total price we could find for <i>any</i> pair of men''s motorcycle boots by $20. They''re available in sizes 6.5 to 13, although not every size/color combination are available.', 18, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2850, '2012-01-30 15:11:00', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300811001106.jpg', 'http://www.skinstore.com/?AID=4198913&PID=1969400&SID=dealshr_15385_1', 'Skinstore extra 20% off sitewide, Clarisonic Mia 2 for $119', '<p> SkinStore is offering <strong>20% off</strong> Storewide via coupon code: <strong>CUPID20</strong>. Free shipping $49 or more. Note that some exclusions may apply. They have the Clarisonic Mia 2 Sonic Cleansing System &#8211; White for<strong> $119 </strong>after coupon. They also have select premium brands items on sale up to 25% off.</p>', 19, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(2851, '2012-01-30 15:13:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300813158081.jpg', 'http://www.neimanmarcus.com/product.jsp?eItemId=prod62360001&itemId=prod62360001&parentId=&cmCat=search&ecid=NMALRpiaqBdsdpmQ&CS_003=5630585', 'Neiman Marcus: select UGG shoes, boots or apparel more than 50% off', '<p> Neiman Marcus is having select UGG shoes, boots or apparel on sale as listed below, most are more than 50% off and the lowest total price we could find:</p> <ul> <li> UGG Dakota Driver Bow Slipper for <strong>$45</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Classic Tall Bomber Jacket Boot for <strong>$81</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Hartley Suede Wedge Boot for <strong>$123</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Annisa Mid-Calf Boot for<strong> $117</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Braided Suede Clog for <strong>$72</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Wool/Cashmere Puffer Jacket for <strong>$267</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Blackfoot Shearling Coat for <strong>$582</strong></li> <li> UGG Australia Poia Down-Fill Vest for <strong>$132</strong></li> </ul>', 21, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2852, '2012-01-30 15:13:15', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300813158925.jpg', 'http://www.menswearhouse.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/Navigation_-1_10601_10051_10051_/Shoes/@/N-1z141g5Z1z141q6Z1z141yjZ1z141ye/dp-1z141q6__Pprice|0?sort=Pprice|0&searchTerm=&searchType=sort&redirectURL=&top=10051', 'Mens Wearhouse 40% off select mens shoes', '<p> Men&#8217;s Wearhouse is taking<strong> 40% off</strong> Rockport , Dockers , and Belvedere men&#8217;s shoes via coupon code &#8220;<strong>40SHOEM</strong>&#8220;. Shipping starts at $8 but orders of $150 or more qualify for free shipping. (Free ship-to-store is also available.) Deal ends January 30.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Fashion'),
(2853, '2012-01-30 16:02:33', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300902337266.jpg', 'http://www.hanes.com/clothing/women/bras/view-all-bras/womens-no-slip-fit-underwire?d1=CSEH&cm_mmc=ComparisonShopping-_-shopzilla.com-_-women%3ESALE!%20bras%3Eview%20all%20bras-_-G327', 'Hanes Clearance: Up to 70% off women''s + extra 20% off 1 item, free shipping', 'Hanes takes <strong>up to 70% off</strong> select women''s apparel in its clearance section. Plus, coupon code "85624" takes an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> one item. Even better, coupon code "86937" bags <strong>free shipping</strong> with no minimum purchase required. Combined, that''s tied with our December mention as the best such stacking discount we''ve seen from Hanes. Sales tax is added where applicable. Notables, with prices and <strong>free shipping</strong> after the coupons above:<ul><li> Hanes Women''s Ultimate Ribbed Button Tank for <strong>$4.79</strong></li><li> Hanes Women''s No Slip Fit Wirefree Bra for <strong>$5.59</strong></li><li> Hanes Women''s No Slip Fit Underwire Bra (pictured) for <strong>$5.59</strong></li><li> Hanes Women''s Signature Chunky Hat for <strong>$5.59</strong></li><li> Hanes Women''s Signature Featherweight Ruched Henley for <strong>$7.99</strong></li><li>see all women''s clearance apparel at Hanes </li></ul>', 19, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(2854, '2012-01-30 16:02:34', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120130/201201300902347892.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/offers/home#!details/68921397252fe74d/DLDTBAO04G1ORHI8;r=IWRldGFpbHMvNjg5MjEzOTcyNTJmZTc0ZA%3D%3D', '$50 Credit at PajamaGram for $25', 'Google Offers offers a $50 PajamaGram Credit for <strong>$25</strong>. That''s tied with our mention from four weeks ago and the fourth time we''ve ever seen such a discount from PajamaGram, which sells sleepwear carepackages. The credit can be redeemed immediately after purchase through April 28. However, it can''t be applied towards shipping, which starts at <b>$10.99</b>. Deal ends January 31.<p>Of note, although this is listed under Google Offers Atlanta, it can be purchased and used by anyone outside of that area.</p>', 17, 'Dealnews Clothing');
