(3012, '2012-01-31 12:02:46', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310502469744.jpg', 'http://bananarepublic.gap.com/?tid=braff552179&ap=2&siteID=brafcid51', 'Banana Republic coupon: 25% off sitewide, stacks with sale', 'Banana Republic takes <strong>25% off</strong> sitewide, including sale items, via coupon code "BRBOOST". That''s among the best discounts we''ve seen from Banana Republic in recent months, although we saw 30% off sitewide two weeks ago. Shipping adds a flat <strong>$7</strong>, or get free shipping on orders of $50 or more. Sales tax is added where applicable and some exclusions apply. Deal ends January 31.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(3013, '2012-01-31 12:07:16', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310507167542.jpg', 'http://www.swarovski.com/Web_US/en/91109/category?AID=10407424&CJPID=2165238&SID=no_refer', 'Valentine''s Day Coupon: 10% Off with purchase of full-priced items of $155 or more @ Swarovski', '<ul><li> Swarovski is having a new valentine''s day coupon: get 10% Off with purchase of full-priced items of $155 or more via coupon code: <strong> VALENTINE2012 （Ends Feb 14）</strong> .</li><li>Free shipping for order over $95. </li></ul>', 18, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
