(3017, '2012-01-31 12:10:58', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310510589787.jpg', 'http://www.origins.com/linkshare.tmpl?siteID=piaqBdsdpmQ-stMalrScmo8ss7Ha3dQsAg&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.origins.com%3Fcm_mmc%3DLinkshare-_-piaqBdsdpmQ-_-null-_-null', 'Origins: FREE Perfect World Antioxidant cleanser with White Tea + free shipping with ANY order', '<p> Origins is offering FREE Perfect World Antioxidant cleanser with White Tea + FREE Shipping with any Origins.com purchase. Enter Code <strong>BONUS1 </strong>at checkout. Offer valid thru 2/4. Note that you can choose another free sample at checkout.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(3018, '2012-01-31 12:11:02', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310511027767.jpg', 'http://www.sephora.com/index.jhtml?om_mmc=aff-linkshare-homepage-piaqBdsdpmQ&_requestid=4503', 'Sephora 17 free samples or free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &#038; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 order', '<p> Sephora is offering a Skincare Sample Bag with 14 samples for free with orders of $25 or more via coupon code &#8220;<strong>TRY14</strong>&#8220;. Plus another three samples given with each order. Shipping starts at $5.95 or get free shipping with orders of $50 or more. The bag includes eye cream, moisturizer, serum, cleansing oil, day cream, and more. Note that you can also receive a free deluxe sample of Buxom Big &amp; Healthy Lip Polish in Katie with $25 purchase via code <strong>LIPLOVE</strong> at checkout.</p>', 21, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(3019, '2012-01-31 12:13:03', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310513037992.jpg', 'http://www.ae.com/web/index.jsp', 'American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle extra 40% off clearance + extra 15% off coupon', '<p> American Eagle Outfitters and aerie by American Eagle are taking an <strong>extra 40% off</strong> clearance items. (Discount is applied in-cart.) Even better, apply  coupon code &#8220;<strong>60255011</strong>&#8221; to get an <strong>additional 15% off</strong>. Shipping starts at $7 or get free shipping with orders of $100 or more.</p>', 18, 'Huaren Fashion'),
