(3032, '2012-01-31 13:11:02', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310611027906.jpg', 'http://www.bergdorfgoodman.com/store/catalog/templates/silo.jhtml?itemId=cat000005&ecid=BGALRTnL5HPStwNw', 'Bergdorf Goodman Beauty Event', '<p> <strong>Bergdorf Goodman</strong> is having a <strong>Rewarding Beauty Event</strong> . Spend $200 on beauty to receive a cosmetic bag with eleven deluxe samples. There are over 40 GWPs during this event. Free Shipping with any order with code <strong>BTYBAG</strong>.</p>', 16, 'Huaren Beauty'),
(3033, '2012-01-31 14:03:16', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310703163820.jpg', 'http://www.meritline.com/coleman-luggage-explorer-42-camping-duffel-red---p-68011.aspx?clickid=VHlmMGtBb0JDeHNBQUNUcTBDMEFBQU9X&source=dealnews', 'Coleman Explorer 42" Camping Duffle Bag for $20 + free shipping', 'Meritline offers the Coleman Explorer 42" Camping Duffel Bag in Red (pictured), model no. CT0398R, Green , model no. CT0398E, Yellow , model no. CT0398Y, or Blue , model no. CT0398N, for <b>$19.99</b> with <b>free shipping</b>. That''s tied with our mention from a week ago and the lowest total price we could find in any color by $13. It measures 42" x 20" x 15" and features 2" nylon wrap-around webbing handles, a front zippered pocket, detachable shoulder strap, and zippered storage pouch.', 14, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(3034, '2012-01-31 14:09:11', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310709111834.jpg', 'http://www.shopjustice.com/?AID=10593114&PID=2138476&utm_content=1880868&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=%28Expired%29+Justice+234x60+Logo+Only&utm_source=cj_affiliate&utm_term=cj', 'Justice Coupons: 40% off Entire Order Online &amp; In-store', '<li> Shipping starts at $5. </li> Available Justice Coupons and Justice Coupon Codes:<br /><li><b>40% off Entire Order Online & In-store</b><br />* Online: Use Justice Coupon Code 779 or 752 [Exp. 02/08] <br />* In-store: In-store Printable Justice Coupon [Exp. 02/08]', 17, 'Dealigg ApparelShoes'),
(3035, '2012-01-31 14:17:33', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310717338792.png', 'https://www.carters.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-Carters-Site/default/Home-Show?id=carters&id=carters&commjunction=carters&cm_mmc=CJCarters-_-552179-_-dealnews.com-_-x', 'Carter''s: 20% off $40 coupon', '20% off $40 coupon Code: SUNNY Note: Exclusions apply. Expires: 01/31/2012', 18, 'dealcoupon Clothing'),
(3036, '2012-01-31 15:03:07', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310803077197.png', 'http://www.sharkstores.com/Jewelry?data1=VHlnQ2Jnb0JDeGdBQUE5dmV0UUFBQUx5&a_aid=8', '1-tcw Ruby and Diamond Pendant Necklace for $116 + free shipping', 'Today only, SharkStores offers this 1-carat total weight Ruby and Diamond Pendant Necklace for $119. Coupon code "3DealForGirl3" cuts it to <b>$116</b>. With <b>free shipping</b>, that''s $72 under the lowest total price we could find for a similar pendant elsewhere. This heart-shaped pendant features 23 round-cut rubies, six round-cut diamonds, 18" 10K white gold rope chain, gift box, and more.', 16, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
(3037, '2012-01-31 15:07:31', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310807315762.png', 'http://www.graveyardmall.com/daily-deal/', '$14.99 ($59.94,75% off) Hanes Women''s Wide-Strap Fitted Tank Top 5-Pack', 'Today only (Jan 30), Graveyard Mall offers the Hanes Women''s Cotton Wide-Strap Fitted Tank Top 5-Pack in assorted colors for <strong>$14.99</strong> with <strong>free shipping</strong>.&nbsp;', 22, 'Dealmoon Clothing'),
(3038, '2012-01-31 15:11:02', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201310811022038.jpg', 'http://www.skinstore.com/?AID=4198913&PID=1969400&SID=dealshr_15385_1', 'Skinstore extra 20% off sitewide, Clarisonic Mia 2 for $119', '<p> SkinStore is offering <strong>20% off</strong> Storewide via coupon code: <strong>CUPID20</strong>. Free shipping $49 or more. Note that some exclusions may apply. They have the Clarisonic Mia 2 Sonic Cleansing System &#8211; White for<strong> $119 </strong>after coupon. They also have select premium brands items on sale up to 25% off.</p>', 17, 'Huaren Beauty'),
