(3127, '2012-02-01 00:02:45', 1, '/public/uploads/day_120131/201201311702451342.jpg', 'http://www.wilsonsleather.com/product/index.jsp?productId=11578466', 'Wilsons Leather: Extra 20% off new arrivals, deals from $80 + free shipping', 'Wilsons Leather cuts an <strong>extra 20% off</strong> select new arrivals. (The discount applies automatically in-cart.) Even better, you can get <strong>free shipping</strong> by signing up for its email list. (Sign up using the link in the upper right, and you''ll be emailed a link to claim free shipping.) It''s the best such discount we''ve seen from Wilsons Leather in recent months. Sales tax is added where applicable. Some exclusions apply. Deal ends February 3. Some best bets in the men''s Big & Tall category, with prices after discount and <strong>free shipping</strong>:<ul><li> Pelle Studio Men''s Big & Tall 2-Button Smooth Lamb Blazer (pictured) for <strong>$199.99</strong></li><li> Pelle Studio Men''s Big & Tall Cooper Leather Zip Front Hipster for <strong>$223.99</strong></li><li> Wilsons Leather Men''s Big & Tall Black Rivet Distressed Leather Jacket w/ Hood for <strong>$239.99</strong></li><li> Wilsons Leather Men''s Big & Tall Wilsons Aviator Leather Jacket for <strong>$263.99</strong></li><li>shop for more new arrivals at Wilsons Leather </li></ul>', 14, 'Dealnews Clothing'),
